NK060(i)002:1: / dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK060(i)002:2: pa'i rgyud kyi khog dbub rin po che 'bar ba'i
NK060(i)002:3: gur zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK060(i)002:4: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK060(i)002:5: rgyud khog dbub rin po che 'bar ba'i gur zhes
NK060(i)002:6: bya ba/ bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK060(i)002:7: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po/
NK060(i)002:8: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse/
NK060(i)002:9: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas/
NK060(i)002:11: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs/
NK060(i)002:12: 'bras bu thams cad kyi thug sa/
NK060(i)002:13: sngar 'das pa'i rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi gshegs shul/
NK060(i)002:14: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam dam pa/
NK060(i)002:15: che ba'i yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)002:16: sems dang ye shes rang snang du ston pa/
NK060(i)002:17: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud dpal gsang ba'i snying po 'di bshad pa'i dbang du bgyis na/
NK060(i)002:19: khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgron me las/
NK060(i)002:20: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi yi rgyud //
NK060(i)002:21: sgro skur med par ston pa ni //
NK060(i)002:22: mtshan byed sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba de //
NK060(i)002:23: mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK060(i)002:25: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi'i rgyud ni/
NK060(i)002:26: sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi chos nyid rang
NK060(i)002:27: bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen
NK060(i)002:28: por ye nas sangs rgyas pa de yin la/
NK060(i)002:29: de mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge rgyud kyi bshad thabs/
NK060(i)002:30: spyi don rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas ston par byed de/
NK060(i)002:31: spyir na rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK060(i)002:32: rgyas rnams kyis gdul bya sems can rnams kyi don
NK060(i)002:33: du/ bstan pa dang theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul dang /
NK060(i)002:34: de dag gi nang nas bstan pa dang theg pa gang yin par bsdus te ngos bzung ba dang /
NK060(i)002:36: dang po bstan pa dang theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:37: rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thugs
NK060(i)002:38: rje che la thabs la mkhas pa rnam pa thams
NK060(i)002:39: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi dgongs pa dang ldan
NK060(i)002:40: pa rnams kyis gdul bya sems can khams gsum dang
NK060(i)002:41: 'khor zhing rgyud drug tu 'khyams pa rnams kyi don
NK060(i)002:42: du bstan pa dang theg pa ji ltar gsung zhe
NK060(i)002:43: na/ gsungs pa'i tshul gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:44: nyon mongs pa la dgongs te gsungs pa dang /
NK060(i)002:45: theg pa'i rkang grangs la dgongs te gsungs pa dang /
NK060(i)002:46: thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:47: dang po nyon mongs pa la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)002:49: ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gnyen por/
NK060(i)002:50: chos stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:53: zhes pas gdul bya sems can rnams kyi rgyud la
NK060(i)002:54: nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi la
NK060(i)002:55: sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod pas/
NK060(i)002:56: de dag 'dul ba'i gnyen por dam pa'i chos stong
NK060(i)002:57: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa bsam gyis
NK060(i)002:58: mi khyab pa zhig gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:59: de dag kyang mdor bsdu na/
NK060(i)002:60: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi cha las gyur pa
NK060(i)002:61: nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por dam pa'i chos
NK060(i)002:62: 'a dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs/
NK060(i)002:63: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi cha las gyur pa
NK060(i)002:64: nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por dam pa'i chos
NK060(i)002:65: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs/
NK060(i)002:66: nyon mongs pa gti mug gi cha las nyi khri
NK060(i)002:67: chig stong gi gnyen por dam pa'i chos mngon pa'i
NK060(i)002:68: sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs/
NK060(i)002:69: nyon mongs pa dug gsum mam lnga la sogs pa
NK060(i)002:70: mtha' dag gi gnyen po rig pa 'dzin pa sngags
NK060(i)002:71: kyi sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs te/
NK060(i)002:72: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)002:73: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)002:74: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)002:75: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)002:76: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)002:77: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)002:78: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)002:79: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)002:80: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)002:81: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK060(i)002:82: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK060(i)002:84: de yang sngar 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:85: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsung ngo //
NK060(i)002:86: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang gsung bar 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)002:87: gnyis pa theg pa'i rkang grangs la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)002:88: 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:90: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:91: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:92: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:93: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:94: bla na med pa sngags kyi theg pas/
NK060(i)002:95: zhes pas theg pa lnga ru 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)002:97: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK060(i)002:98: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK060(i)002:99: zhes pas theg pa bzhi ru 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)002:101: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK060(i)002:102: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK060(i)002:103: gsum du nges par bstan pa ste //
NK060(i)002:104: kun 'byung 'dren dang dka' thub rig /dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK060(i)002:105: zhes theg pa gsum du 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)002:107: theg pa rnams pa gnyis yin te //
NK060(i)002:108: mtshan nyid rgyu'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:110: zhes pas theg pa gnyis su 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)002:112: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK060(i)002:113: theg pa dag la thug pa med //
NK060(i)002:114: sems ni yongs su gyur pa na //
NK060(i)002:115: theg pa med cing 'gro ba med //
NK060(i)002:116: theg pa gcig tu nga smra ste //
NK060(i)002:117: theg pa'i rnam gzhag yod ma yin //
NK060(i)002:118: byis pa rnams ni yongs drang phyir //
NK060(i)002:119: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad do //
NK060(i)002:121: ji srid 'du shes med kyi bar //
NK060(i)002:122: theg pa'i sgo yang de las med //
NK060(i)002:123: ji srid 'du shes gnas ma thag /theg pa'i sgo yang bsam mi khyab //
NK060(i)002:124: ces pa sa theg pa gcig tu 'dus par yang gsungs shing /
NK060(i)002:125: theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab par yang gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:126: gsum pa thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)002:127: 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:128: de dag thams cad kyang gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i
NK060(i)002:129: dbang gis phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung
NK060(i)002:130: ba 'dzin pa 'khrul pas las 'dogs pa dang /
NK060(i)002:131: las dang las kyi 'bras bu chud mi za ba dang /
NK060(i)002:132: las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos/
NK060(i)002:134: gos su med pa ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK060(i)002:136: theg pa chung ngus nyon mongs pa spong 'gegs dang /
NK060(i)002:137: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa la sbyong ba dang /
NK060(i)002:138: sngags phyi rgyud pa la lhar bsgyur ba dang /
NK060(i)002:139: nang pa bskyed rdzogs gnyis la dbang du byed pa dang /
NK060(i)002:140: a ti la spang gnyen ro gcig pa'i tshul gyis te/
NK060(i)002:141: mdor na nyon mongs pa rang kha ma'i rtog pa
NK060(i)002:142: 'joms par byed pa'i gnyen po'ang lnga'am drug tu 'dus
NK060(i)002:143: par gsungs so // spyi don gnyis pa de dag
NK060(i)002:144: gi nang nas bstan pa dang theg pa gang yin
NK060(i)002:145: par bsdus te ngos bzung ba ni/
NK060(i)002:146: theg pa'i rkang grangs mang du gsungs kyang yongs su
NK060(i)002:147: grags pa'i dbang du theg pa rim pa dgur 'dus
NK060(i)002:148: te/ 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:149: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK060(i)002:150: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK060(i)002:151: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK060(i)002:152: ces pas theg pa rim pa dgu las/
NK060(i)002:153: rgyud gzhung 'di ni mtshan nyid sde gsum yang ma yin/
NK060(i)002:154: phyi rgyud sde gsum yang ma yin/
NK060(i)002:155: nang rgyud du ngos bzung ngo //
NK060(i)002:157: bskyed pa sku'i rgyud byin che bar ston pa ma
NK060(i)002:158: h+aa yo ga /rdzogs pa gsung gi rgyud gzhal gsal
NK060(i)002:159: bar ston pa a nu yo ga /bskyed rdzogs gnyis
NK060(i)002:160: su med par ston pa a ti yo ga las/
NK060(i)002:161: 'dir ma h+aa yo gar ngos bzung ngo //
NK060(i)002:162: 'di la rgya gar na tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad du yod pa las/
NK060(i)002:163: bod du bsgyur ba la sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad/
NK060(i)002:165: de dag gi man ngag phra mo drug cu rtsa bzhi dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)002:166: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta chen po bi ma la mi tra'i zhal snga nas/
NK060(i)002:167: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog gis bsgyur ba las/
NK060(i)002:169: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad nang nas kyang rtsa ba'i rgyud du gyur pa/
NK060(i)002:170: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kha na nyid nges pa zhes par ngos bzung ngo //
NK060(i)002:171: spyi don gsum pa de ltar ngos bzung ba'i rgyud
NK060(i)002:172: gzhung 'di nyid bshad thabs kyi yan lag du zhe
NK060(i)002:173: na/ khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgron me las/
NK060(i)002:174: phas kyi lan gdab 'bru snon tshig /khog dbub sa bcad bzhi ru gsungs //
NK060(i)002:175: zhes pas khog dbub pa stong thun gyi don dang
NK060(i)002:176: sbyar te bshad pa dang gcig /sa bcad pa dkyus
NK060(i)002:177: kyi don dang sbyar te bshad pa dang gnyis/
NK060(i)002:178: 'bru snon pa tshig gi don dang sbyar te bshad pa dang gsum/
NK060(i)002:179: gnas skabs brgal lan gyi don dang sbyar te bshad pa dang bzhis ston pa las/
NK060(i)002:180: dang po khog dbub pa stong thun gyi don dang sbyar te bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)002:181: rgyud thams cad kyi spyi don lnga'i sgo nas 'chad/
NK060(i)002:182: man ngag thams cad rtsis 'go lnga nas 'chad pa yin pas/
NK060(i)002:183: 'dir spyi don lnga'i sgo nas bshad la/
NK060(i)002:184: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs ji ltar gnas tshul/
NK060(i)002:185: de ltar ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul/
NK060(i)002:186: de la thams cad mkhyen po'i thugs rjes gzigs tshul/
NK060(i)002:187: gzigs nas thugs rje bskyed tshul/
NK060(i)002:188: thugs rje bskyed nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad tshul bstan pa dang lnga'i 'chad de/
NK060(i)002:189: de ltar yin par gang gis shes na/
NK060(i)002:190: 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:191: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang chos thams cad
NK060(i)002:192: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du gcig
NK060(i)002:193: pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas dbyer med na'ang /
NK060(i)002:195: 'gro ba'i rnam par rtog pa ma rig pa las/
NK060(i)002:196: 'gro ba lnga'i rigs bsam gyis mi khyab pa smin pa la zhes pas 'khrul tshul dang /
NK060(i)002:197: thugs rje chen po zhes pas thugs rjes gzugs tshul dang /
NK060(i)002:198: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas zhes pas thugs rje bskyed tshul dang /
NK060(i)002:199: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do zhes pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad tshul dang lnga las/
NK060(i)002:200: spyi don dang po sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs ji ltar 'dug tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:201: ya ki rgyal ba kun tu bzang po nas/
NK060(i)002:202: ma ki 'jag mig gi srin bu yan chad du/
NK060(i)002:205: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por sangs rgyas pa yin te/
NK060(i)002:206: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u bco lnga pa las/
NK060(i)002:208: mtha' yas dkyil 'khor ma lus kun //
NK060(i)002:209: rgyal ba'i yum gyi dbyings su thim //
NK060(i)002:210: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK060(i)002:212: rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:213: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK060(i)002:214: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK060(i)002:215: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK060(i)002:219: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di/
NK060(i)002:220: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK060(i)002:222: spyi don gnyis pa de ltar ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:223: gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas su gnas kyang /
NK060(i)002:224: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa na/
NK060(i)002:225: rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ste/
NK060(i)002:226: rang ngo rang gis ma shes pa'o //
NK060(i)002:227: dpe rigs mnyam pa'i rgyal bu phrug gu dmangs su 'khyams pa lta bu'o //
NK060(i)002:228: de ltar yin par yang spong rdor las/
NK060(i)002:229: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas kyang //
NK060(i)002:230: mun pas bsgribs te ngo ma shes //
NK060(i)002:232: ye nas da ltar gnas mod kyang //
NK060(i)002:233: ma rig pa yi ling thog gis //
NK060(i)002:234: gsal ba'i sgron me bsgribs gyur te //
NK060(i)002:237: sems rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba yin yang /
NK060(i)002:238: nges pa'i shes pas nges par ma bya pa ni/
NK060(i)002:239: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK060(i)002:241: der ma zad lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang ngo ma shes pas de ka la/
NK060(i)002:245: thibs se sdod dam zhe na/
NK060(i)002:247: rkyen kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas/
NK060(i)002:251: gzung 'dzin sna tshogs su snang nas 'khrul lo //
NK060(i)002:252: dpe rgyal bu dwa phrug de yang /
NK060(i)002:253: dmangs su 'khyams pa rang ngo ma shes pa tsam la mun ne thom me sdod dam zhe na/
NK060(i)002:257: lag tu khyi gsod kyi ber ka thogs nas/
NK060(i)002:258: dmangs phal ba'i spyod ngan sna tshogs byed do //
NK060(i)002:259: de ltar yin par yang rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:260: phyin ci log las 'jol nyog spyod //
NK060(i)002:261: gzung 'dzin don la shin tu chags //
NK060(i)002:265: chos dang bdag dang dngos po rnams //
NK060(i)002:266: ngo bo yod la sogs brtags pas //
NK060(i)002:267: rtog pa sgyu ma'i rlung gyur te //
NK060(i)002:269: de ltar ma rig pa gnyis kyis 'gags pa'i lam
NK060(i)002:270: dang bral zhing sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba'i nyes
NK060(i)002:272: rang bzhin dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK060(i)002:273: thabs dang lhan cig mi gnas par //
NK060(i)002:277: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:279: dpe rgyal bu dwa bu de rigs ma nyams pa
NK060(i)002:280: rgyal bu yin par ston pa'i blon rgyus ma dang
NK060(i)002:281: bral ba'am/ rgyus med lam mkhan dang bral ba lta bu'o //
NK060(i)002:282: spyi don gsum pa de la thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs rjes gzigs tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:284: log par rtog btags rnam dag cing //
NK060(i)002:285: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK060(i)002:286: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK060(i)002:287: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK060(i)002:288: zhes pas de la thugs rjes gzigs tshul gsum du dbye na/
NK060(i)002:289: dbyings las mi gzhan pa las ji lta ba mkhyen
NK060(i)002:290: pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya 'dul byed ma dmigs
NK060(i)002:291: par gzigs tshul ni/ rgyas pa las/
NK060(i)002:292: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs ldan pa //
NK060(i)002:293: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK060(i)002:294: mtha' dang dbus kyang brtag tu med //
NK060(i)002:297: yang dag rtogs pas rab brtags na //
NK060(i)002:298: rang bzhin med las cir yang 'grub //
NK060(i)002:300: ye shes las mi gzhan pa las ji snyed pa
NK060(i)002:301: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis ma 'gags par gzigs tshul
NK060(i)002:303: mtho dman kun gyi gzugs rnams dang //
NK060(i)002:304: blo med byang chub skur snang bas //
NK060(i)002:305: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK060(i)002:306: sna tshogs kha dog dbyibs su snang //
NK060(i)002:308: yang shes rab chen po'i mig ldan pas //
NK060(i)002:309: mtho dman gnas dang lam drug gnas //
NK060(i)002:310: so so'i de bzhin 'khor bar gzigs //
NK060(i)002:312: dbyings ye shes dbyer med de ji lta ji snyed
NK060(i)002:313: dbyer med du mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis dbyer med
NK060(i)002:314: du gzigs tshul ni/ rgyas pa las/
NK060(i)002:315: rnam par rtog pa mi mnga' ste //
NK060(i)002:316: de yis mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK060(i)002:318: de ltar thugs rjes gzigs tshul gsum la brtag pa yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:319: yul yod med dbyer med gsum las/
NK060(i)002:321: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes gzung 'dzin can du 'gyur ba'i skyon/
NK060(i)002:323: dbu ma ye shes rgyun chad pa ltar/
NK060(i)002:324: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes rgyun chad par 'gyur ba'i skyon/
NK060(i)002:326: thugs rje gang la gang gis gang ltar gzigs te/
NK060(i)002:327: gzigs pa'i tha snyad rang mi 'thad do zhe na/
NK060(i)002:328: de la lan 'debs lugs gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:332: thugs rje'i yul yod par sgro mi 'dogs/
NK060(i)002:334: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi
NK060(i)002:335: chos thams cad gzhon nu ma la pra phab pa
NK060(i)002:336: bzhin du rtog med rang gsal du gzigs so //
NK060(i)002:339: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i khams gsum pa'i sems las byung ba thams cad/
NK060(i)002:340: lag mthil gyi skyu ru ra gzhin du gsal mkhyen ma 'gags par snang /
NK060(i)002:342: ji ltar snang yang bden pa'i ngo bos stong /
NK060(i)002:344: shes bya'i gshis la thugs rjes skye ba'i yul khams gsum gyi sems can dang /
NK060(i)002:345: skye mkhan rnam mkhyen gyi sangs rgyas gnyis dmigs su med pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:346: dmigs su med pa de thugs rjer ci 'gyur zhe na/
NK060(i)002:347: thugs rje ni snying rje'i zhes pa yin la/
NK060(i)002:348: snying rje ni sdug bsngal las skyob pa zhig yin te/
NK060(i)002:349: de yang sems can dang chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje ni byis pa'i snying rje yin la/
NK060(i)002:350: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje ni snying rje chen po ste/
NK060(i)002:351: sdug bsngal mtha' dag las skyob pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:352: de yang rdzogs pa chen po sgom pa don drug pa las/
NK060(i)002:353: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med rtogs na //
NK060(i)002:354: thugs rje chen por skyes zhes de la bya //
NK060(i)002:356: de ltar yin pa kas thugs rjes gzigs pa'am skyes pa'i tha snyad mi 'grub bo zhe na/
NK060(i)002:358: dngos po'i gshis la sangs rgyas dang sems can ma dmigs pa las ma dmigs pa ltar gzigs shing /
NK060(i)002:359: de ltar ma shes pas zag pa bzhi'i rgya la
NK060(i)002:360: 'thum pa rnams grol bar byed pa'i thabs kyang yin
NK060(i)002:361: te/ dper na skyes bu mngon shes can zhig gi drung na/
NK060(i)002:362: skyes bu gzhan zhig gnyid du song ba'i rmi lam du/
NK060(i)002:363: rnag mdze rab tu 'bar bas lus sems sdug bsngal bar gyur pa la/
NK060(i)002:364: skyes bu mngon shes can de'i thugs yul la/
NK060(i)002:365: gnyid du song ba'i skyes bu de la mdze ma byung ba yang mkhyen/
NK060(i)002:366: mdze ma byung bzhin du kho mdze nad byung ba'i snang bas nyam thag pa yang mkhyen/
NK060(i)002:367: de las grol bar byed pa'i thabs gnyid sad par byed pa yang mkhyen pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)002:368: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)002:369: tshul 'di dag ma go ba kha cig /sangs rgyas kyi ye shes dang /
NK060(i)002:370: sems can gyi 'khrug rtog la lhan cig dmigs nges zhugs ma zhugs kyi brtag pa byed do //
NK060(i)002:371: gyi na'i brgal lan du rig par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:372: spyi don bzhi pa de ltar gzigs nas thugs rje skyed tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:373: re zhig slob dpon bi ma la'i dgongs pa ltar bzhi ru dbye na/
NK060(i)002:375: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK060(i)002:377: zhes pas dang po rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje skye tshul chu bo chen po'i gzhung lta bu ni/
NK060(i)002:378: dper na chu bo chen po'i gzhung dbyar dgun dang /
NK060(i)002:379: ston dpyid med par breng nge 'byung ba ltar/
NK060(i)002:380: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i chen po rnams kyi thugs rje skye ba ni rgyun chad med de/
NK060(i)002:381: de yang le'u dang po'i bsdu ba las/
NK060(i)002:382: ye shes dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang //
NK060(i)002:384: gnyis pa rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje skye tshul nyi ma'i 'od zer lta bu ni/
NK060(i)002:385: dper na nyi ma nam mkha'i mthongs su shar bas
NK060(i)002:386: 'od zer dro 'jam rtsol med du ngang ngam shugs
NK060(i)002:388: rgyal ba'i thugs rje la rtsol rtog dang skyo dub med par ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba'o //
NK060(i)002:389: de yang bcu gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:392: gsum pa bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i rkyen gyi
NK060(i)002:393: thugs rje skye tshul sdug 'bod slong ba la ster
NK060(i)002:394: ba lta bu ni/ dper na slong mo ba rnams
NK060(i)002:395: kyi smre sngags kyi 'o dod 'bod pas pham phab
NK060(i)002:397: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams la yang bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa na/
NK060(i)002:398: thugs rje khyad par can skye ste/
NK060(i)002:400: lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi rtogs na'ang /
NK060(i)002:401: ma 'ongs pa'i don du rgyud gsung bar zhus pa/
NK060(i)002:402: e ma ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK060(i)002:404: ston pas lan gnang ba ni/
NK060(i)002:405: e ma bde gshegs snying po las/
NK060(i)002:407: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK060(i)002:409: 'di nyid dngos su nyan pa'i skal ba yod pa rnams la dgyes pa tshul drug gi sgo nas gsungs/
NK060(i)002:410: nyan pa'i skal ba med pa rnams la/
NK060(i)002:411: lam stegs kyi ston pa thub pa drug tu sprul nas gsungs pa yin skad/
NK060(i)002:412: bzhi pa yul dang 'phrad pa'i rkyen gyi thugs rje skye tshul/
NK060(i)002:413: long sprang gi smre sngags bton pa bas kyang /
NK060(i)002:414: mdze nad gdug pa can gyis zin pa'i mdze pho la lhag par ster ba lta bu ni/
NK060(i)002:415: dper na spyir sdug yongs thams cad snying rje'i yul yin yang /
NK060(i)002:416: khyad par du mdze pho rkang chad lag rdum dang
NK060(i)002:417: phrad na bzod thabs med pa'i snying rje skye ba
NK060(i)002:418: bzhin/ spyir 'gro drug gi sems can thams cad thugs rje'i yul yin yang /
NK060(i)002:419: khyad par du ru dra thar pa nag po lta
NK060(i)002:420: bu nyon mongs pa dug gsum rags par smin pa
NK060(i)002:421: la thugs rje khyad par can skye ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:422: 'di nyid kyi bco lnga pa las/
NK060(i)002:423: de sngon bsten pa'i stobs kyi thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs nas thugs rjes 'dul bar gyur to //
NK060(i)002:425: spyi don lnga pa thugs rje skyes nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:427: spyir theg pa lngas don mdzad tshul dang /
NK060(i)002:428: khyad par du gsung gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyud 'di nyid kyis don mdzad tshul gnyis las/
NK060(i)002:429: theg pa lngas don mdzad pa la skol mod lnga pa sbyor la/
NK060(i)002:430: khyad par rgyud 'di nyid kyis don mdzad tshul bzhi ru bzhed kyang /
NK060(i)002:431: rje sgrub phug pa'i bzhed kyis spyir sku gsung thugs
NK060(i)002:432: yon tan phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i don
NK060(i)002:433: mdzad pa dang / khyad par du gsung gsang ba'i
NK060(i)002:434: bstan pa rgyud 'di nyid kyis don mdzad pa gnyis
NK060(i)002:435: mdzad pa dang / su bzhed do // dang po ni rgyas pa'i le'u don gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:436: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK060(i)002:437: phyoogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK060(i)002:438: 'gro ba'i phrin las bsam mi khyab //
NK060(i)002:439: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK060(i)002:440: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK060(i)002:441: gdul bya rnams ni chud ma zos //
NK060(i)002:442: ngan song sbyong zhing byang chub zhing //
NK060(i)002:443: ye shes tshogs rdzogs kun tu ston //
NK060(i)002:445: khyad par du gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyud 'di nyid kyis don mdzad pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:446: 'di'i byin rlabs kyi don mdzad pa dang /
NK060(i)002:447: 'di nyid dngos kyi don mdzad pa'o //
NK060(i)002:448: dang po 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:449: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las thugs
NK060(i)002:450: rje chen pos byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i rig
NK060(i)002:451: pa'i skye bu thub pa drug /de bzhin gshegs pa
NK060(i)002:452: thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje
NK060(i)002:453: las 'thon to // zhes pas rgyud 'di nyid kyi
NK060(i)002:454: ston pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs
NK060(i)002:458: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK060(i)002:459: gsung dang bzhis don mdzad pa ste/
NK060(i)002:460: de yang skus don mdzad pa ni/
NK060(i)002:466: ston pa'i thub pa zhes pa'i bar gyis ston //
NK060(i)002:467: thugs kyi mdzad pa yang 'di nyid las/
NK060(i)002:468: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang //
NK060(i)002:470: mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang /
NK060(i)002:472: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa ni/
NK060(i)002:474: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK060(i)002:476: bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to //
NK060(i)002:477: zhes pa'i bar gyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:478: gsung gi mdzad pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:481: thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:482: dang po ni 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:485: bla na med pa'i theg pa zhes pa'i bar gyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:488: mtshan nyid ji lta bu zhe na/
NK060(i)002:489: 'og nas gong du 'degs par byed pa'i don gyis na theg pa zhes pa'am/
NK060(i)002:490: sa lam las gzhan pa'i rtogs pas myang 'das kyi
NK060(i)002:491: khung 'khyer ba'i don gyis na theg pa zhes bya'o
NK060(i)002:492: // de lta bu'i theg pa la rnam grangs nges pa'i ji lta bu yod snyam na/
NK060(i)002:493: gdul bya'i blo'i rim pa'i dbang du/
NK060(i)002:494: theg pa'i rnam grangs kyang ma nges par snang ste/
NK060(i)002:495: theg pa rim pa dgu dang /
NK060(i)002:500: bsam gyis mi khyab pa la sogs par snang yang /
NK060(i)002:501: skabs 'dir theg pa'i grangs ji ltar nges na/
NK060(i)002:505: gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad kyang bsdu na 'og nas 'byung ba 'di lta ste/
NK060(i)002:506: gdul bya'i blo dang mos pa tha dad pa 'dul
NK060(i)002:507: ba'i dbang gis theg pa'i rnam grangs kyang lngar snang
NK060(i)002:508: ba'o // de yang lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:510: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u lnga pa rigs kyang so sor dbye ba las/
NK060(i)002:511: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spong byed pa //
NK060(i)002:512: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK060(i)002:513: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK060(i)002:514: tshangs gnas la sogs skye ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK060(i)002:515: zhes pas lha zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)002:516: mi zhes pa'i ming ni 'dod rgyal te/
NK060(i)002:517: 'jug pa'i sgo mi dge bcu spong pa'i sgo nas
NK060(i)002:518: 'jug /spyad bya dge ba bcu dang du len zhing
NK060(i)002:519: spyod/ rtog pa'i lta ba las rgyu 'bras kyi mi bslu bar rtogs/
NK060(i)002:520: bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin tshad med bzhi dang /
NK060(i)002:522: de ltar bsgoms pas 'bras bu lha dang mi'i gnas rigs/
NK060(i)002:523: 'dod khams kyi mtho ris gnas bcu dang /
NK060(i)002:524: khams gong ma gnyis kyi stod rigs su 'degs par
NK060(i)002:525: byed pa'am thob par byed pa'i don gyis na lha
NK060(i)002:527: de ltar 'bras bu thob pa ltar du snang nas don mdzad pa yang /
NK060(i)002:528: rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs kyi shugs las snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:529: de ltar na lha dang mi'i theg pa 'di/
NK060(i)002:530: theg pa mtshan nyid pa yin nam zhe na/
NK060(i)002:531: 'das pa'i theg pa mtshan nyid pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)002:532: gtan tshigs ni lam rim las/
NK060(i)002:533: bzhi yi theg pa dang por zhog /ces pas nges 'byung bzhi'i theg pa la/
NK060(i)002:534: dang po lha mi'i theg pa ni/
NK060(i)002:535: 'das pa'i theg pa rnams 'byung ba'i gazhi'am/
NK060(i)002:536: rgyu yin par zhog cig ces pas/
NK060(i)002:537: 'di'i 'bras bu lha mi'i stod rigs nas/
NK060(i)002:538: 'das pa'i theg pa mtshan nyid pa/
NK060(i)002:539: nyan thos kyi theg pa la sogs pa'i theg pa rim pa dgur 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:540: de yang theg pa rim pa dgu ni/
NK060(i)002:543: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:544: phyi mtshan nyid kyi theg pa sde gsum mo //
NK060(i)002:547: yo ga'i theg pa gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:548: sngags phyi rgyud kyi theg pa gsum mo //
NK060(i)002:551: a ti yo ga'i theg pa gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:552: sngags nang rgyud kyi theg pa gsum mo //
NK060(i)002:553: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:556: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spong ba yi //
NK060(i)002:557: ye shes bcu drug cha sbyang rab zhi ba //
NK060(i)002:558: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim par sbyangs nas ni //
NK060(i)002:559: nyon mongs dgra rnams 'joms pa'i sa ru 'gro //
NK060(i)002:560: zhes pas nyan thos kyi sgra don nam nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:561: gzhan brten thos sgrog ces pa ste/
NK060(i)002:562: slob dpon gzhan la brten cing /
NK060(i)002:563: de las thos pa'i don gzhan la sgrog pa'i phyir nyan thos zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)002:564: 'jug pa'i sgo 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK060(i)002:565: 'jug /spyad bya'i tshul khrims so sor thar pa rigs
NK060(i)002:566: brgyad kyi bsrung bya'am/ khyad par du khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu rang don du spyod/
NK060(i)002:567: rtogs pa'i lta ba gang zag gi bdag rang bzhin med par rtogs/
NK060(i)002:568: bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin bden pa bzhi po re re yang /
NK060(i)002:569: chos shes chos bzod gnyis rjes shes rjes bzod gnyis te ye shes bcu drug rim pa bzhin bsgom/
NK060(i)002:570: de ltar bsgoms pas gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rgyun zhugs dang /
NK060(i)002:571: lan cig phyir 'ong mi 'ong gnyis mthar thug rgyan bcas dang rgyan med kyi dgra bcom pa ste/
NK060(i)002:572: lhag bcas dang lhag med kyi myang 'das kyi gnas
NK060(i)002:573: su 'degs par byed pa'am thob par byed pa'i don
NK060(i)002:574: gyis na nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:575: de ltar 'bras bu thob pa ltar du snang nas
NK060(i)002:576: don mdzad pa yang rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs
NK060(i)002:578: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:580: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul shes shing //
NK060(i)002:581: dngos po'i gzugs la thogs med rab tu 'jug /dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs //
NK060(i)002:582: byang chub sa bgrod yid bzhin bden ba mchog /ces
NK060(i)002:583: pas rang byang chub kyi sgra don nam nges tshig
NK060(i)002:584: ni/ sbyor lam bzod pa 'bring po nas rigs bya ste/
NK060(i)002:585: rang gi 'bras bu ma thob kyi bar du rkyen
NK060(i)002:586: slob dpon gzhan la mi ltos par rang gi shes
NK060(i)002:587: rab kyis dur khrod kyi keng rus la brtags nas
NK060(i)002:589: rang gi byang chub rang gis thob par 'dod pas rang byang chub ces pa'am/
NK060(i)002:590: slob dpon gyi lung med par bdag nyid gcig pu'i
NK060(i)002:591: phyir sangs rgyas pas na rang sangs rgyas zhes bya'o
NK060(i)002:592: // 'jug pa'i sgo rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi sgo
NK060(i)002:593: nas 'jug /spyad bya'i tshul khrims khrims nyis brgya lnga
NK060(i)002:594: bcu rang don du spyod pa nyan thos dang mtshungs
NK060(i)002:595: // la/ khyad par du theg pa chen po med pa'i sar/
NK060(i)002:596: rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung gi sgo nas gzhan don shas 'ga' spyod/
NK060(i)002:597: rtogs pa'i lta ba bdag med pa phyed dang gnyis rang bzhin med par rtogs/
NK060(i)002:598: bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin ni rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK060(i)002:599: lugs 'byung bkag nas lugs ldog stong pa bcu gnyis
NK060(i)002:600: khrigs chags su bsgom/ de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu bse ru lta bu gcig pur gnas pa'am/
NK060(i)002:601: tshogs na spyod pa ne tso lta bur khyu lding
NK060(i)002:602: bas mthar thug gi dgra bcom pa yid bzhin bde
NK060(i)002:603: ba mchog gi sar 'degs par byed pa'am thob par
NK060(i)002:604: byed pa'i don gyis na rang byang chub kyi theg
NK060(i)002:605: pa dang / de ltar 'bras bu thob pa ltar
NK060(i)002:606: du snang nas don mdzad pa yang rgyud 'di nyid
NK060(i)002:608: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:610: bdag med gnyis rtogs pha rol phyin rdzogs pa'i //
NK060(i)002:611: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK060(i)002:612: sangs rgyas sa bgrod go 'phang thob pa'i lam //
NK060(i)002:613: bden pa gnyis kyis rab tu thob par 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:614: zhes pas byang chub sems dpa'i sgra don nam nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:615: bdag don du byang chub pa gzhan don la sems dpas na byang chub sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)002:616: 'jug pa'i sgo bden pa gnyis sam smon 'jug gnyis
NK060(i)002:617: kyi sgo nas 'jug /spyad bya'i tshul khrims pha rol
NK060(i)002:618: tu phyin pa drug gam bcu gzhan don 'ba' zhig
NK060(i)002:619: tu spyod/ rtogs pa'i lta ba gang zag dang chos
NK060(i)002:620: kyi bdag gnyis rang bzhin med par rtog /bsgom bya'i
NK060(i)002:621: tu spyod/ ting nge 'dzin ni/ sa bcu rim gyis
NK060(i)002:622: spros bral du bsgoms pas sgrib gnyis bag chag dang
NK060(i)002:623: tu spyod/ ting nge 'dzin ni/ bcas pa spong la/
NK060(i)002:624: de ltar bsgoms pa'i gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu sa
NK060(i)002:625: tu spyod/ ting nge 'dzin ni/ bcas pa spong la/
NK060(i)002:626: bcu rim gyi bgrod/ mthar thug gi 'bras bu bcu
NK060(i)002:627: gcig kun tu 'od kyi sar 'degs par byed pa'am
NK060(i)002:628: thob par byed pa'i don gyis na byang chub sems
NK060(i)002:630: de ltar 'bras bu thob pa ltar du snang nas
NK060(i)002:631: don mdzad pa yang rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs
NK060(i)002:633: bla na med pa sngags kyi theg pas zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)002:634: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK060(i)002:635: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK060(i)002:636: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK060(i)002:637: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK060(i)002:638: zhes pas bla na med pa sngags kyi theg pa'i sgra don nam nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:639: gong gi theg pa de dag las kyang lta sgom spyod 'bras mchog tu gyur pas na/
NK060(i)002:640: bla na med pa'i mchog tu gyur pa sngags kyi theg pa ste/
NK060(i)002:642: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:643: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NK060(i)002:644: dang po phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa la gsum las/
NK060(i)002:645: dang po bya ba'i rgyud kri ya'i theg pa ni/
NK060(i)002:646: 'jug pa'i sgo khrus dang gtsang sbra'i sgo nas 'jug /spyad bya'i rdzas dkar gsum mngar gsum la spyod/
NK060(i)002:647: rtogs pa'i lta ba sems dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma dang bral bar rtogs/
NK060(i)002:648: bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin ni mtshan bcas lha ye shes sems dpa' rje bo dang /
NK060(i)002:649: bdag dam tshig sem dpa' khol po'i tshul gyis mchod
NK060(i)002:650: pa phar 'bul zhing dngos grub tshur zhu ba dang
NK060(i)002:651: / mtshan ma med pa bden pa gnyis res mos su sgom/
NK060(i)002:652: de ltar bsgom pa'i 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje
NK060(i)002:653: 'dzin pa'i sar 'degs par byed pa'am thob par byed
NK060(i)002:654: pa'i don gyis na kri ya'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:655: gnyis pa spyod pa'i rgyud u pa ya'i theg pa ni/
NK060(i)002:656: 'jug dang spyod pa bya ba'i rgyud dang mthun/
NK060(i)002:657: lta ba dang sgom pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud dang mthun/
NK060(i)002:658: de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu rigs bzhi rdo rje
NK060(i)002:659: 'chang gi sar 'degs par byed pa'am thob par byed
NK060(i)002:660: pa'i don gyis na u pa ya'i theg pa dang
NK060(i)002:661: / gsum pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud yo ga'i theg pa ni/
NK060(i)002:662: 'jug pa'i sgo ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas 'jug /spyad bya'i dam rdzas kha yar la spyod/
NK060(i)002:663: rtogs pa'i lta ba sems rang rig rang gsal dag pa lha so bdun gyi rang bzhin du rtogs/
NK060(i)002:664: bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin mtshan bcas lha ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK060(i)002:665: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' grogs po'am mnyam po'i tshul du bsgoms nas/
NK060(i)002:666: skyes dang skyes lan gyi tshul du phan tshun mchod pa mnyam por 'bul ba dang /
NK060(i)002:667: mtshan ma med pa'i bden pa gnyis mgo mnyam du bsgom/
NK060(i)002:668: de ltar bsgom pa'i 'bras bu rigs lnga stug po
NK060(i)002:669: bkod pa'i sar 'degs par byed pa'am thob par byed
NK060(i)002:670: pa'i don gyis na yo ga'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:671: de ltar 'bras bu thob pa ltar du snang nas don mdzad pa yang /
NK060(i)002:672: rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs kyi shugs las snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:673: gnyis pa nang pa thabs kyi rgyud rnal 'byor chen
NK060(i)002:674: po bla na med pa'i rgyud kyi theg pa la
NK060(i)002:675: yang / bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga /rdzogs pa
NK060(i)002:676: a nu yo ga /bskyed rdzogs gnyis su med par
NK060(i)002:677: ston pa a ti yo ga'i theg pa dang gsum
NK060(i)002:678: yang / du ston pa las/ nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i skol mdo na/
NK060(i)002:679: gzhung hril po yin pas sbyar mi dgos gsung yang /
NK060(i)002:680: ma sbyar na ngos mi zin pas/
NK060(i)002:682: 'jug pa'i sgo thabs shes gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug
NK060(i)002:683: /spyad bya'i rdzas dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la 'jol
NK060(i)002:684: nyog tu spyod/ rtogs pa'i lta ba bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por rtogs/
NK060(i)002:685: bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin lha dang rtogs pa dbyer med du bsgom/
NK060(i)002:686: de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu pad+ma can dang /
NK060(i)002:687: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar 'degs par
NK060(i)002:688: byed pa'i don gyis na bskyed rim gtso che bar
NK060(i)002:689: ston pa ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:690: de las kyang rdzogs rim gtso che bar ston pa a nu yo ga'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)002:691: de las kyang gnyis su 'dzin pa'i rtsol ba dang
NK060(i)002:692: bral nas bskyed rdzogs gnyis su med par ston pa
NK060(i)002:693: a ti yo ga'i theg pa'o //
NK060(i)002:694: de ltar 'bras bu thob pa ltar du snang nas don mdzad pa yang /
NK060(i)002:695: rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs kyi shugs las snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:696: gnyis pa nyon mongs pa la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)002:698: ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)002:702: theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i skabs su bshad par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:703: gsum pa thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)002:705: de dag thams cad kyang zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)002:706: mthar thug go zhes pa'i bar te/
NK060(i)002:707: rgyas par gzhung bshad kyi skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:708: khyad par du gsung gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyud 'di nyid dngos kyi don mdzad pa la bzhi ste/
NK060(i)002:709: rgyud 'di nyid ji ltar byung tshul gyi rgyud lung bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)002:710: de ltar rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag rnam rim
NK060(i)002:711: pa bzhin brgyud pa'i rgyud sde zab mo 'di nyid
NK060(i)002:712: che ba brgyad dang ldan tshul bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)002:713: che ba brgyad ldan gyi rgyud 'di nyid gang zag phal gyi yul ma yin zhing /
NK060(i)002:714: dbang po yang rab kyi spyod yul du bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)002:715: dbang po yang rab kyi spyod yul rgyud sde zab
NK060(i)002:716: mo 'di nyid kyi gnas tshul snang ba bzhi'am rgyud
NK060(i)002:718: gnas pa ltar khog dbub pa'o //
NK060(i)002:719: de la dang po rgyud sde zab mo'i 'di ji ltar byung ba'i tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:720: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag gsum //
NK060(i)002:721: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK060(i)002:722: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK060(i)002:724: rgyal ba dgongs par brgyud pa ni/
NK060(i)002:725: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos/
NK060(i)002:726: rgyal tshab rigs lnga la brgyud/
NK060(i)002:727: rigs lngas rgyal sras sems dpa' la sogs pa lhan cig pa'i 'khor la brgyud pa'o //
NK060(i)002:728: rig 'dzin rig par brgyud pa ni/
NK060(i)002:729: mi ma yin pa la brgyud pa dang /
NK060(i)002:730: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa'o //
NK060(i)002:731: dang po ni thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas/
NK060(i)002:732: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bar du rgyal ba rigs gsum gyis brgyud pa/
NK060(i)002:734: spyan ras gzigs kyi sgrub pa/
NK060(i)002:735: phyag rdor gyis spyod pa bstan zer yang /
NK060(i)002:736: gsang sngags kyi lta spyod sgrub pa gsum ka'i don/
NK060(i)002:737: 'jam dpal gzhon nu mdzes pa'i sku dang ldan pa
NK060(i)002:738: des lha rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun
NK060(i)002:739: par chos bstan te/ 'jam dpal rdo rjee rnon pos/
NK060(i)002:740: lha grangs ldan phyogs skyong la bshad/
NK060(i)002:742: des skye rgu'i bdag po tshangs pa la/
NK060(i)002:743: des tshangs pa kun grol la/
NK060(i)002:744: des tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin la/
NK060(i)002:745: des dbang po brgya byin la/
NK060(i)002:746: des lha'i rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad/
NK060(i)002:747: de ltar gyur pa'i lha rnams kyang byang chub sems dpa'i rigs 'dzin cing /
NK060(i)002:748: rgyal ba rnams kyi gdung 'tshob par gyur to //
NK060(i)002:749: spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman gyi sku dang ldan pa des/
NK060(i)002:750: klu gdug can rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun pas/
NK060(i)002:751: klu rgyal mgrin nag po la bshad/
NK060(i)002:752: de klu mo kha 'dul ma la/
NK060(i)002:753: des klu mo 'dul tshang ma la/
NK060(i)002:754: des klu yid 'ong dga' ba la/
NK060(i)002:756: des klu tshom bu 'bum sde la/
NK060(i)002:757: de ltar klu rnams kyang gong ltar gyur to //
NK060(i)002:758: phyag na rdo rje 'jigs tshul bsdigs pa'i sku dang ldan pa des/
NK060(i)002:759: gnod sbyin rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun pa/
NK060(i)002:760: gnod sbyin grags ldan mchog skyong la bshad/
NK060(i)002:761: des gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la/
NK060(i)002:762: des gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje la/
NK060(i)002:763: de gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong la/
NK060(i)002:764: des gnod sbyin tshom bu 'bum sde la/
NK060(i)002:765: de ltar gnod sbyin rnams kyang gong ltar gyur to //
NK060(i)002:766: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa ni/
NK060(i)002:771: srin po lang ka mgrin bcu/
NK060(i)002:772: mi las skal ldan li tsa dri ma med par
NK060(i)002:773: grags pa la sogs pa rig pa 'dzin pa 'dus
NK060(i)002:774: pa'i 'khor la/ ma la ya'i rtser gsungs shing brgyud do //
NK060(i)002:775: gang zag rna bar brgyud pa ni/
NK060(i)002:776: gsang bdag gis rim la ya'i rtser chos kyi 'khor
NK060(i)002:777: lo bskor ba'i byin rlabs rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas
NK060(i)002:778: bdun shar cing / dngos su po ti dang glegs bam gyi char babs so //
NK060(i)002:779: de yang rmi ltas bdun ni/
NK060(i)002:780: ri ma la ya de'i shar lho na/
NK060(i)002:781: tri sham a su ra'i brag phug ces bya ba/
NK060(i)002:782: phug rin po che zur brgyad yod pa/
NK060(i)002:783: sgo rin po che zla gam du yod pa/
NK060(i)002:784: logs la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo rang byung ba/
NK060(i)002:785: logs la brag seng ge dkar po khyi tshugs lta bu yod pa/
NK060(i)002:786: mkhar yang dog gsum rim dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)002:787: steng na bya ka lan+ta ka'i tshang bcas nas chos
NK060(i)002:788: thams cad thig le nyag gcig tu sgrogs pa yod
NK060(i)002:789: pa/ rtsa ba na bdud rtsa'i chu mig rang rdol
NK060(i)002:790: du yod pa mdun na me tog gi snam bu
NK060(i)002:791: pa/ yod pa/ shing yal ga phyogs bzhir gyes pas dus bzhi'i dgra las skyob pa ltar du yod pa/
NK060(i)002:792: shing de'i me tog dang 'bras bu sman du gyur te/
NK060(i)002:793: zos pas nad sna tshogs sel ba/
NK060(i)002:794: de lta bu'i nyams dga' ba'i gnas khang der/
NK060(i)002:795: las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams kyis ni bgrod du thar la/
NK060(i)002:796: las dang skal bar mi ldan pa rnams kyis ni
NK060(i)002:797: mi thar ba'i bar khang na skal ldan rgyal po
NK060(i)002:798: dzahgasanga sngags phyi rgyud la sgrub pa mdzad kyin bzhugs
NK060(i)002:799: pa la/ rmi ltas bdun zhag re re la rmi yang skad/
NK060(i)002:800: zhag gcig la rmi yang skad de/
NK060(i)002:802: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon te/
NK060(i)002:804: gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs/
NK060(i)002:805: gsung gi gnas nas bstan pa dang theg pa'i sgra bsgrags pas/
NK060(i)002:806: gdul bya thams cad kyis go bar mdzad/
NK060(i)002:807: thugs kyi gnas nas rdo rje 'bar ba byung nas/
NK060(i)002:809: spyi bo'i gtsug nas nyi ma byung nas rgyal po'i spyi gtsug tu thim par rmis so //
NK060(i)002:810: de yang dgongs 'dus kyi 'grel pa lung bstan rdo rje las/
NK060(i)002:811: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK060(i)002:814: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams nyi ma dang zla ba la chibs/
NK060(i)002:815: phyag na gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan
NK060(i)002:816: pa bsnams na sems can thams cad la chos kyi
NK060(i)002:818: de yang chos kyi bgro ba mdzad pa dang //
NK060(i)002:821: nam mkha' la sprin gser gyi kha dog can ni chags/
NK060(i)002:822: snang srid gsal ba'i glog 'khyug /cho 'phrul gyi 'brug
NK060(i)002:823: sgra dam pa chos kyi sgra ru di ri ri
NK060(i)002:824: sgrog pa rmis te/ de yang chos sgra chen po sgrog pa dang //
NK060(i)002:827: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun babs te/
NK060(i)002:828: sa phyogs thams cad chag chag btab/
NK060(i)002:829: gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs nas/
NK060(i)002:830: kun kyang rdo rje rnal 'byor zhes gsang sngags kyi sgra di ri ri sgrog pa zhig rmis so //
NK060(i)002:831: de yang bdud rtsi char du babs pa dang //
NK060(i)002:834: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas rin po che'i sgrom gyi nang na/
NK060(i)002:835: rin po che mthing gi shog bu la/
NK060(i)002:836: gser gyi rgya rang nan du bris pa'i po ti dang glegs bam/
NK060(i)002:837: skar mda' thang la babs pa tsam du lhung bar rmis so //
NK060(i)002:838: de yang rin cen char du babs pa dang //
NK060(i)002:841: po ti glegs bam de rnams la rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams/
NK060(i)002:843: la la ni bskor ba byed/
NK060(i)002:844: la la ni bstod pa byed pa'i sgra sgrog pa zhig rmis so //
NK060(i)002:845: de yang p+au dza rgya chen byas pa dang //
NK060(i)002:848: nam mkha'i mthongs nas gzugs su ma grub pa lung ston pa'i sgra/
NK060(i)002:849: las dang skal bar rab ldan zhing //
NK060(i)002:850: bsod nams chen po'i dra ma khyod //
NK060(i)002:851: sprul pa ji ltar lung bstan bzhin //
NK060(i)002:852: rgyal ba 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i //
NK060(i)002:853: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /skal ldan khyod la sgrog par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:855: der rgyal po mnal sad de/
NK060(i)002:856: mkhar gyi yang thog tu sku 'chag tu byon pas/
NK060(i)002:857: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje'i sku rgyu rin po
NK060(i)002:858: chen smug po las grub pa khru gang pa zhig
NK060(i)002:859: bzhugs kyin yang skad/ de la phyag dang bskor ba lan gsum byas/
NK060(i)002:860: zhabs spyi bo'i gtsug tu blangs te/
NK060(i)002:861: e ma ngo mtshar mchog gi sku //
NK060(i)002:862: 'dren pa mchog gi dpal lags gang //
NK060(i)002:863: mos pa'i yid kyi lha mchog khyod //
NK060(i)002:864: las kyi 'brel ba'i lha mchog khyod //
NK060(i)002:865: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK060(i)002:866: gsungs te yi dam gyi lhar bzung nas zla ba bdun du sgrub pa mdzad pas/
NK060(i)002:867: po ti dang glegs bam rmi lam du byung ba rnams mngon sum du babs shing /
NK060(i)002:868: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyi snang ba dpe char shar ba yin skad/
NK060(i)002:869: der rgyal pos po ti dang glegs bam de rnams la brtags pa rtogs par 'dug kyang /
NK060(i)002:870: gdul bya gzu lum ras chod can dag dgags par bya ba'i phyir du/
NK060(i)002:871: ma rtogs pa ltar gnang nas/
NK060(i)002:872: 'jig rten gyi khams na mkhyen pa su che zhes dris pas/
NK060(i)002:873: za hor gyi yul na rgyal po u pa r+aa dza zhes bya ba mkhyen rgya che'o zhes zer te/
NK060(i)002:876: rgyal po'i thugs kyi rtog pa ma chod kyis dogs nas 'byon du ma bzhed skad/
NK060(i)002:877: po ti dang glegs bam rnams rta dang glang po
NK060(i)002:878: che la khol la tong shig ngas brtag go gsungs
NK060(i)002:879: nas/ po ti dang glegs bam rnams stag sgro dang gzig sgro'i nang du bcug nas/
NK060(i)002:880: a ka ru dang du ru ka la sogs spos sna tshogs dang /
NK060(i)002:881: gdug dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa p+au dza sna tshogs dang bcas te spyan drangs te/
NK060(i)002:882: khong gi brtag pas tshig gcig kyang brda ma 'jal skad/
NK060(i)002:883: sngon gyi mtshan rtags dang sbyar na rgyal po nyid
NK060(i)002:884: rang gis rtogs par 'gyur ro gsungs nas tshur spyan
NK060(i)002:885: drangs skad/ yang rgyal po nyid kyis brtags pas rtogs par 'dug kyang /
NK060(i)002:886: ma rtogs pa ltar gnang nas/
NK060(i)002:887: yang 'jig rten gyi khams na mkhyen pa su che zhes dris pas/
NK060(i)002:888: sangs rgyas rin cen mang gi sbrul pa dge slong
NK060(i)002:889: ku ku r+aa dza zhes bya ba mkhyen rgya che'o
NK060(i)002:890: zer nas/ spyan 'dres du btang bas rgyal po'i thugs
NK060(i)002:891: kyi rtog pa ma chod kyis dogs nas 'byon du
NK060(i)002:892: ma gnang bar po ti dang glengs bam stag sgro
NK060(i)002:893: dang gzig sgro'i nang du bcug /a ka ru dang
NK060(i)002:894: du ru ka la sogs pa spos sna tshogs dang
NK060(i)002:895: zer nas/ / gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa
NK060(i)002:896: mchod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs dang bcas pas spyan
NK060(i)002:897: zer nas/ / drangs nas/ dge slong ku ku r+aa dza nyid kyis brtags pas/
NK060(i)002:898: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud bya ba de'i nang nas/
NK060(i)002:899: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs sgrub pa'i le'u'am/
NK060(i)002:900: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'ura rtogs te/
NK060(i)002:901: zla ba bdun du sgrub pa mdzad pas/
NK060(i)002:902: rdo rje sems dpa' ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo la byon te/
NK060(i)002:904: sid+d+hi ci 'dod ces gsungs pa las/
NK060(i)002:905: bstan pa dang theg pa mtha' dag rtogs pa'i dngos grub zhu zhes zhus pas/
NK060(i)002:906: phyag na rdo rjes lung ston par 'gyur gyi gsungs nas mi snang bar song skad/
NK060(i)002:907: yang zla ba bdun sgrub pa mdzad pas/
NK060(i)002:908: phyag na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas/
NK060(i)002:909: rdo rje lan gsum spar nas/
NK060(i)002:910: spong len brtul zhugs spyod pa'i dbang //
NK060(i)002:911: dge bar bskur na sdig pa med //
NK060(i)002:913: rtsol ba dab bcas pa mtshan nyid kyi theg pa spangs nas/
NK060(i)002:914: rtsol ba med pa gsang sngags kyi theg pa nyams su len pa khyod la/
NK060(i)002:916: theg pa thams cad rdzogs par dbang bskur ro //
NK060(i)002:917: tshig gi bstan pa de dag dge bsnyen li tsa
NK060(i)002:918: byi dri ma med pa la zhus shig ces lung
NK060(i)002:919: bstan no // ku ku r+aa dzas gsang ba'i bdag po'i bka' bzhin bsgrub shing /
NK060(i)002:920: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)002:921: tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad du phye nas/
NK060(i)002:922: skal ldan rgyal po dzahl gsungs/
NK060(i)002:923: tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad la/
NK060(i)002:926: glang po che rab 'bog /gla po che chur zhugs/
NK060(i)002:935: yon tan gyi rgyud gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:939: phrin las kyi rgyud gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:942: k+ai la ya yig 'bru bcu gnyis kyi rgyud/
NK060(i)002:944: de dag thams cad kyi spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud/
NK060(i)002:945: dam tshig sa ma ya 'bum sde bkod pa'i rgyud/
NK060(i)002:946: rdo rje thabs kyi zhags pa'i rgyud de/
NK060(i)002:947: de ltar tan+t+ra sde chen po bco brgyad po rgyal po dzahs/
NK060(i)002:949: des sras mo go ma sa la/
NK060(i)002:950: des khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza la/
NK060(i)002:951: des ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub la/
NK060(i)002:952: des rdo rje bzhad pa la/
NK060(i)002:953: des za hor gyi rgyal po pra b+ha hasti la/
NK060(i)002:954: des slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba la/
NK060(i)002:955: des slob dpon bi ma la mi tra la sogs pa pan+di ta lnga brgya la gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:956: de'i dus na bod kyi yul na chos kyi skyong
NK060(i)002:957: ba'i rgyal po mnga' bdag ral pa can bya ba
NK060(i)002:958: bzhugs pas/ khong gis rgya gar gyi yul na rje mi la bkur zhes bya ba la/
NK060(i)002:959: mchod gnas pan+di ta lnga brgya tsam zhig bzhugs pa gsan nas/
NK060(i)002:961: cog ro klu'i dbang phyug /nyang po klu'i rgyal mtshan dang gsum la gser phye ma bre do/
NK060(i)002:962: gser gyi pa tra gnyis skyes su bskur nas/
NK060(i)002:963: skyes lan du pan+di ta sgra don tshig la mkhas pa gcig bardzanga bar zhu zhes zhu ba phul bas/
NK060(i)002:964: rje mi la bkur gyi mchod gnas pan+di ta lnga brgya rtsa gcig po bsags nas/
NK060(i)002:965: chos ston yon dang bcas pa re drangs te/
NK060(i)002:966: khyed rnas kyi nang nas pan+di ta sgra don tshig
NK060(i)002:967: la mkhas pa zhig /bod kyi yul du chos skyong
NK060(i)002:968: ba'i rgyal po'i mchod gnas la gshegs par zhu 'tshal
NK060(i)002:969: zhes zhus pas/ yar gyi nyis brgya lnga bcus kyang
NK060(i)002:970: mar gzigs mar gyi nyis brgya lnga bcus kyang yar
NK060(i)002:971: zhes zhus pas/ gzigs/ de rnams kyi dbus na slob dpon bi ma la mi tra bzhugs pas/
NK060(i)002:972: khong gis bod du 'byon par thugs kyis dgongs nas/
NK060(i)002:973: bang chen pa mi gsum gyis dpal gyi bsam yas su spyan drangs shing /
NK060(i)002:974: lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis chos mang du bsgyur te/
NK060(i)002:975: khyad par du gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras/
NK060(i)002:977: a tsar+ya rma rin chen mchog gis mtshan nyid dang sgyu 'phrul bsgyur/
NK060(i)002:980: de dag gi man ngag rnams dang bcas pa bsgyur skad/
NK060(i)002:982: sems dang ye shes rang snang du ston pa sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po/
NK060(i)002:983: rol pa mngon par brjod pa lha mo sgyu 'phrul/
NK060(i)002:984: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par ston pa sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa/
NK060(i)002:985: phrin las rdzogs par ston pa sgyu 'phrul bzhi bcu pa/
NK060(i)002:986: dbang gtso bor ston pa sgyu 'phrul bla ma/
NK060(i)002:987: yon tan mthar phyin par ston pa sgyu 'phrul bcu pa/
NK060(i)002:988: sde snod yongs la khyab pa ston pa 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po/
NK060(i)002:989: dam tshig mchog tu ston pa sgyu 'phrul le lag dang brgyad do //
NK060(i)002:991: grol lam rim dang cir car ston pa ye shes snying po dang rdo rje me long gnyis/
NK060(i)002:992: thabs lam rim dang cir car ston pa sgyu 'phrul thal ba dang /
NK060(i)002:994: de rnams las bshad rgyud sde bzhi ma gtogs pa rnams/
NK060(i)002:995: lo ts+aa ba rma rin cen mchog gis/
NK060(i)002:996: gtsug ru rin cen gzhon nu dang /
NK060(i)002:998: de gnyis kyis dar rje dpal gyi grags pa dang /
NK060(i)002:999: zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan gnyis la bshad/
NK060(i)002:1000: de gnyis ni dar rje dpal gyi grags pa mkhas/
NK060(i)002:1001: bla ma yang gang zag yin pas brtags la bya gsungs nas/
NK060(i)002:1002: bla ma'i bka' bzhin mi mdzad pas/
NK060(i)002:1005: zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan ni bla ma'i bka' bzhin mdzad pas/
NK060(i)002:1007: 'gro phan shin tu che bar byung skad/
NK060(i)002:1009: zhang gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad gsan nas/
NK060(i)002:1010: 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ma gtogs pa rnams so ye shes dbang phyug la gsungs/
NK060(i)002:1011: des dbang thung byang chub rgyal mtshan la/
NK060(i)002:1012: des kong btsun shes rab ye shes la/
NK060(i)002:1013: des gtsang ger thung shes rab tshul khrims la/
NK060(i)002:1014: des nyang shes pa mchog la/
NK060(i)002:1015: des nyang ye shes 'byung gnas la/
NK060(i)002:1016: des lha rje 'ug bya lung pa la gsungs/
NK060(i)002:1018: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches/
NK060(i)002:1019: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho la/
NK060(i)002:1020: des sras ye shes rgya mtsho la/
NK060(i)002:1021: des nyang ban shes rab mchog la/
NK060(i)002:1024: des 'bar rtse mo bzhi rtse lkog dang lnga/
NK060(i)002:1025: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs pa gsungs/
NK060(i)002:1027: ra sa'i zhang 'gos chung pa mkhyen rgya'i rtse mo/
NK060(i)002:1028: shangs mtsho nya'i bzang sgom shes rab rgyal po sgom sgrub kyi rtse mo/
NK060(i)002:1029: ban gyi mi nyag 'byung grags bshad pa'i rtse mo/
NK060(i)002:1030: thag gi bde bshegs rgya bo lta dgongs kyi rtse mo'o //
NK060(i)002:1031: de la slob ma ka ba bzhi/
NK060(i)002:1033: gdung phran sum cu rtsa gnyis/
NK060(i)002:1034: yus po che'i mi gnyis la sogs pa mang du byung ngo //
NK060(i)002:1035: de yang ka ba bzhi la/
NK060(i)002:1036: gong bu'i skyo ston sh+aaka ye rdzogs chen gyi ka ba/
NK060(i)002:1037: nag po ri gseb kyi 'dan tig chos sh+aaka phrin sgrub kyi ka ba/
NK060(i)002:1038: skyed lung gi yang khyed bla ma mdo'i ka ba/
NK060(i)002:1039: chu bar gyi glan sh+aakya bzang po sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1041: sna nam gyi gnubs ston bag ma/
NK060(i)002:1043: ne ser gyi skyo chos seng /
NK060(i)002:1049: yus po che mi gnyis ni/
NK060(i)002:1052: lha rje zur chung gi sras/
NK060(i)002:1053: sh+aakya rdo rje rgyan mtshan dang /
NK060(i)002:1056: yab kyi slob ma ka bzhi gdung brgyad kun la gsan kyang /
NK060(i)002:1057: gzhug slan nya tshal ba lag gtugs skad/
NK060(i)002:1058: lha rje sh+aakya seng ges sgro phug bzung ba'i dus su/
NK060(i)002:1059: slob ma mang du byon kyang /
NK060(i)002:1060: de rnams kyi nang nas bu chen nag po bzhi/
NK060(i)002:1067: mda' nag gtsug tor dbang phyug go //
NK060(i)002:1068: ston pa chen po bzhi ni/
NK060(i)002:1079: slob dpon nye ston gnyis kyis/
NK060(i)002:1080: slob dpon gtsang nag 'od 'bar la gsungs/
NK060(i)002:1081: des bla ma sna bzhi pa g.yu ston sangs rgyas la/
NK060(i)002:1082: des bla ma rgya gab gong pa la/
NK060(i)002:1083: des bla ma sna bzhi pa'i sras g.yung ston chos mgon la/
NK060(i)002:1084: des bla ma lce ston sgrub pa 'bum la/
NK060(i)002:1085: des zur thams cad mkhyen pa chos rje chen po byams pa seng ge la/
NK060(i)002:1086: des g.yung ston rdo rje dpal dang /
NK060(i)002:1087: 'jam pa'i dbyangs chen po bsam grub rdo rje la/
NK060(i)002:1090: bla ma mes ston mgon po la gsungs/
NK060(i)002:1091: des bla ma bro chen po shes rab rgyal mtshan la/
NK060(i)002:1092: des bla ma rta nag pa bdud 'dul 'bum la/
NK060(i)002:1093: des bla ma mda' ston chen po yongs 'dzin sh+aakya 'phel la/
NK060(i)002:1094: des zur thams cad mkhyen pa chos rje byams pa seng ge la/
NK060(i)002:1095: des khams gsum mun pa'i khrod du 'khyams pa la
NK060(i)002:1096: ye shes kyi sgron me spor bar mdzad pa 'jam
NK060(i)002:1097: pa'i dbyangs bsam grub rdo rje la/
NK060(i)002:1098: des mtshan lan gcig thos pa'am yid la dran pa tsam gyis/
NK060(i)002:1099: 'khor ba dang ngan song gi sdug bsngal mtha' dag sel zhing /
NK060(i)002:1100: srid pa dang zhi ba'i bde 'bras phun sum tshogs
NK060(i)002:1101: pa stsol bar mdzad pa mtshungs med chos kyi rje
NK060(i)002:1103: gsang sngags kyi bstan pa'i mnga' bdag snyigs ma'i dus
NK060(i)002:1104: kyi rdo rje 'chang chen po 'gro ba'i mgon po
NK060(i)002:1105: sgrol ma ba sangs rgyas rin cen rgyal mtshan dpal
NK060(i)002:1106: bzang po mi 'gyur bstan pa'i rdo rje gnyis la
NK060(i)002:1107: gsungs/ des mkhyen rab dang thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal la/
NK060(i)002:1108: des lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho la/
NK060(i)002:1109: yang brgyud lugs gcig la 'gos lo la brgyud mi dgos par/
NK060(i)002:1110: sgrol ma ba sangs rgyas rin chen gyis/
NK060(i)002:1112: des sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i rnal 'byor/
NK060(i)002:1113: des se ston rin cen rgyal mtshan la/
NK060(i)002:1115: lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho la/
NK060(i)002:1116: des se ston rin cen rgyal mtshan la/
NK060(i)002:1117: des gnyags ston nam mkha' rgyal mtshan la/
NK060(i)002:1118: des mkhas grub chen po phun tshogs rab brtan la/
NK060(i)002:1119: des mkhyen dang brtse ba'i mnga' bdag dus gsum gyi
NK060(i)002:1120: rgyal ba kun 'dus kyi ngo bo bka' drin srid
NK060(i)002:1121: mtha'i bar du 'khor ba med pa bdag cag gi
NK060(i)002:1122: rtsa ba'i bla ma 'bro ston chen po nam mkha'
NK060(i)002:1123: phrin las la/ des bdag 'bro'i sngags 'chang nam mkha'
NK060(i)002:1124: chos dbang la bka' drin du stsal ba lags so
NK060(i)002:1125: phrin las la/ // gnyis pa de ltar brgyud pa
NK060(i)002:1126: gsum dang ldan pa'i chos 'di che ba du dang
NK060(i)002:1127: phrin las la/ // ldan zhe na/ khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgroon me las/
NK060(i)002:1128: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK060(i)002:1129: gzhan las spags pa che ba brgyad //
NK060(i)002:1131: gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba brgyad dang ldan pa yin te/
NK060(i)002:1132: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po yin pas na nges
NK060(i)002:1133: par che ba gzi ldan gsal ba'i nyi ma lta
NK060(i)002:1134: bu'o // de yang rgyas pa'i le'u lnga bcu pa las/
NK060(i)002:1135: gsang ba'i snying po nges pa 'di //
NK060(i)002:1136: gsang sngags kun gyi rgyal po yin //
NK060(i)002:1138: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin pas na
NK060(i)002:1139: nges par che ba dbus kyi ri bo mchog rab
NK060(i)002:1140: lta bu'o // de yang rgyas pa'i le'unga lnga pa las/
NK060(i)002:1141: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK060(i)002:1142: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK060(i)002:1143: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK060(i)002:1144: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK060(i)002:1146: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung khung yin pas na che ba 'byung ba nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK060(i)002:1147: de yang 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1148: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK060(i)002:1149: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK060(i)002:1150: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK060(i)002:1151: phyogs bcu kun tu rab grags pa //
NK060(i)002:1152: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK060(i)002:1154: lung thams cad kyi spyi 'grel yin pas na nges
NK060(i)002:1155: par che ba nam mkhas snang srid kyi go phye
NK060(i)002:1157: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK060(i)002:1158: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK060(i)002:1161: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i bzhed
NK060(i)002:1162: phugs yin pas na nges par che ba rgyal po'i
NK060(i)002:1163: bka' gsang thob pa'i mi lta bu'o //
NK060(i)002:1164: de yang bcu gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1165: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa ste //
NK060(i)002:1166: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK060(i)002:1167: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK060(i)002:1168: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK060(i)002:1170: 'bras bu thams cad kyi thugs yin pas na nges
NK060(i)002:1171: par che ba yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK060(i)002:1172: che'i lta bu'o // de yang 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1173: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK060(i)002:1174: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK060(i)002:1176: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gshegs shul yin
NK060(i)002:1177: pas na nges par che ba stong gi shul lta
NK060(i)002:1178: bu'o // de yang 'di nyid kyi bcu gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1179: 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK060(i)002:1180: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK060(i)002:1181: brnyes nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:1183: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam yin
NK060(i)002:1184: pas na nges par che ba khri'i lam lta bu'o
NK060(i)002:1189: gsum pa gang zag gi yul yin pa snod kyi tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:1190: spyir blo rtsal rab kyi yul du gyur pa yin te/
NK060(i)002:1192: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul de //
NK060(i)002:1193: skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK060(i)002:1196: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po dang /
NK060(i)002:1197: sbyangs pa'i dbang po rnon po gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:1198: dang po ni don lnga pa las/
NK060(i)002:1199: yangs la rgya che gting zab pa'i //
NK060(i)002:1200: shes rab zab pas rtogs par 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:1202: de phyir blo can rnams kyis brtson //
NK060(i)002:1204: gnyis pa ni bco lnga pa las/
NK060(i)002:1205: yon tan mchog gi snying po 'di //
NK060(i)002:1206: rtog ge'i spyod yul yod ma yin //
NK060(i)002:1207: zab cing rgya che rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK060(i)002:1208: gsal ldan brtan pa'i spyod yul te //
NK060(i)002:1211: thos bsam sgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK060(i)002:1212: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis gzung //
NK060(i)002:1214: bzhi pa rgyud kyi don ji ltar gnas tshul du ltar khog dbub pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1216: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya yi //
NK060(i)002:1217: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK060(i)002:1218: rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par bzhag /gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo ni //
NK060(i)002:1220: des na snang ba bzhi dag tu //
NK060(i)002:1221: lung rig kun las gsal bar bshad //
NK060(i)002:1222: ces pas snang ba bzhi'am rgyud gsum du gnas pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1224: snang bzhi rgyud gsum spyi'i go don brgal lan dang bcas te bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)002:1225: bye brag tu phye ste rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1228: brgal lan gyi sgo nas mtha' yongs su dpyod par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:1229: dang po go don gzhag pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1230: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba'am rgyud ces bya ste/
NK060(i)002:1231: gzhi ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhi/
NK060(i)002:1232: rang bzhin ni bcos bslad dang bral ba/
NK060(i)002:1233: snang ba ni rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1234: de dag la skabs kyi rgyud ces bya ste/
NK060(i)002:1235: gang zhig dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel ba dang ldan pas na rgyud do //
NK060(i)002:1237: gzhi la shes bya yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang zhing /
NK060(i)002:1238: gzhi dang lam gnyis shes bya shes byed du 'brel la/
NK060(i)002:1239: gzhi dang 'bras bu gnyis bdag nyid gcig par 'brel ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1240: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba'am rgyud ni/
NK060(i)002:1241: thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga bskyed pa'am skyed du rung ba gcig gdul bya/
NK060(i)002:1242: 'jug cing bgrod pa byed pa zhig lam pa/
NK060(i)002:1243: bstan pa blo dang 'tshams par snang ba zhig snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1244: de ka la skabs kyi rgyud ces kyang 'dogs te/
NK060(i)002:1245: lam la bgrod pa yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang zhing /
NK060(i)002:1246: lam dang gzhi gnyis shes byed dang shes byar 'brel la/
NK060(i)002:1247: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis thob byed dang thob byar 'brel ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1248: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'am rgyud ni/
NK060(i)002:1249: gang zhig smin pa zhig 'bras bu/
NK060(i)002:1250: nar son pas na bde gshegs/
NK060(i)002:1251: rtogs pa'i rig pa sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1252: de ka la skabs kyi rgyud ces kyang 'dogs te/
NK060(i)002:1253: 'bras bu la thob bya yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang zhing /
NK060(i)002:1254: 'bras bu dang gzhi bdag nyid gcig par 'brel la/
NK060(i)002:1255: 'bras dang lam gnyis thob bya thob byed du 'brel bas na rgyud do //
NK060(i)002:1256: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1257: yul can gnyis med las log cing gnyis su rtog
NK060(i)002:1258: pas na log rtog /de ma yin pa la der
NK060(i)002:1259: bzung bas 'khrul pa/ las dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1260: de la 'brel pa dang dgos pa med pas na/
NK060(i)002:1261: 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni snang ba yin kyang rgyud ma yin no //
NK060(i)002:1263: rang rig pa thams cad du rtsa la ma 'gags
NK060(i)002:1264: par snang ba zhig gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba
NK060(i)002:1265: yin nam ma yin/ ma yin na/
NK060(i)002:1267: rang rig pa thams cad rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba ni rang bzhin gyi snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1269: yin na de'i steng na snang ba gsum po snang ngam mi snang /
NK060(i)002:1270: mi snang na rtsal mi 'gags par snang ba dang 'gal la/
NK060(i)002:1271: snang na gsum du phye ba dgos med du thal/
NK060(i)002:1274: gzhi'i steng du 'char gzhi tsam du snang la/
NK060(i)002:1275: bye brag gsal bar mi snang byas pas skyon las grol lo //
NK060(i)002:1276: bstan pa blo dang 'tshams par snang ba gdul bya'i snang ba yin nam ma yin/
NK060(i)002:1277: ma yin na rgyas pa'i rigs khyad dbye ba las/
NK060(i)002:1278: chos kyi dbyings kyi kun la khyab pa yi //
NK060(i)002:1279: bla med theg pa bsam yas gsungs pa yang //
NK060(i)002:1280: so sor rang rig blo la snang bar zad //
NK060(i)002:1282: yin na de nyams su blangs pas sngags mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob bam mi thob/
NK060(i)002:1283: mi thob na lam nyams su blangs pa la don med par thal/
NK060(i)002:1285: thos bsam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK060(i)002:1286: rang byung sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK060(i)002:1288: thob na mu stegs rtag chad kyang thob par thal/
NK060(i)002:1290: rtag chad gnyis su gang gis blo zhen pa //
NK060(i)002:1291: don gyi snying po nyid las gol bar gsungs //
NK060(i)002:1292: zhes pas gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)002:1293: bstan pa blo dang 'tshams par snang ba zhig lam gyi snang ba yin la/
NK060(i)002:1294: de nyams su blangs pas sngags kyi 'bras bu la las dngos su thob/
NK060(i)002:1295: la las brgyud nas thob bo byas pas skyon las grol lo //
NK060(i)002:1296: rtogs pa'i rig pa sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK060(i)002:1297: 'khor du rang snang ba zhig 'bras bu bde gshegs
NK060(i)002:1298: kyi snang ba yin nam min/
NK060(i)002:1299: ma yin na lung dang 'gal la/
NK060(i)002:1300: yin na mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin chos can/
NK060(i)002:1301: 'dir yang mthar thug pa'i 'bras bur thal/
NK060(i)002:1303: yi ge 'khor lo sngon gzigs na //
NK060(i)002:1305: 'dod lam ma yin pas gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)002:1306: rtogs pa'i rig pa mthar thug pa zhig sku dang
NK060(i)002:1307: ye shes su snang ba de 'bras bu'i snang ba
NK060(i)002:1308: yin no // byas pas skyon las log cing gnyis
NK060(i)002:1309: su bzung bas 'khrul pa'i snang ba yin nam ma
NK060(i)002:1310: yin no // yin/ ma yin na lung dang 'gal la/
NK060(i)002:1311: yin na 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du thal/
NK060(i)002:1314: zhes pas gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)002:1315: las dang log rtog gi blo snang ba zhig 'khrul snang yin yang /
NK060(i)002:1316: 'khrul par snang ba'i snang ba de nyid shes bya'i gshis la ma grub pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)002:1317: 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du mi 'gyur ro byas pa skyon las grol lo //
NK060(i)002:1318: yang snang bzhi gcig gam tha dad ce na/
NK060(i)002:1319: snang ba bzhi po ngo bo bde gshegs snying po las ma g.yos par gcig la/
NK060(i)002:1321: gzhi ni ma rtogs pas 'khrul pa yin/
NK060(i)002:1322: 'khrul pa ni ma rtogs pa 'khrul pa yin/
NK060(i)002:1323: lam pa ni rtogs bzhin 'khrul pa yin/
NK060(i)002:1324: 'bras bu ni rtogs pas 'khrul pa yin pas tha dad do //
NK060(i)002:1325: gnyis pa snang ba bzhin bye brag tu phye ste rgyas par bshad na gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:1326: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang sbyar te bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)002:1327: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud dang sbyar te bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)002:1328: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba 'bras bu thob tshul dang sbyar te bshad pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1329: spyi don dang po gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1331: bcing med rnams par grol med pa'i //
NK060(i)002:1332: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK060(i)002:1334: gzhi 'ching grol med pa'i rig pa rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1337: gang du dgos pa gang nges dang //
NK060(i)002:1338: ngo bo dmigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1342: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs gzung ba/
NK060(i)002:1345: gzhi chos nyid ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas su yod pas/
NK060(i)002:1346: lhan cig pa dang go che ba'i 'khor gyis shes su btub/
NK060(i)002:1347: rtogs su btub pa'i dgos ched yod de/
NK060(i)002:1348: yungs kar la mar nag lhun grub tu yod pas
NK060(i)002:1349: btags btsags byas nas mar nag 'byung ba lta bu'o
NK060(i)002:1351: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung khungs sam gzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:1353: chos thams cad rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK060(i)002:1354: bden pa dbyer med spyood yul dang bral bar ye
NK060(i)002:1355: nas gnas pa'o // de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i don lnga pa las/
NK060(i)002:1356: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK060(i)002:1357: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ste //
NK060(i)002:1360: rnam rtog kun gzhi lam yin la //
NK060(i)002:1361: rang bzhin med pa don gyi gzhi //
NK060(i)002:1363: snang dang mi snang gnyis ka min //
NK060(i)002:1364: yod med gnyis ka dbyer med de //
NK060(i)002:1367: 'du byas snang ba'ang rdo rje nyid //
NK060(i)002:1370: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK060(i)002:1371: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK060(i)002:1372: ces pa'i lung du mas gsal lo //
NK060(i)002:1373: bzhi pa don gyi dmigs gzung ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1375: de yang rnam gsum gnas tshul bzhag /ces pas/
NK060(i)002:1378: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1379: don dam skye 'gag med par mnyam pa ni //
NK060(i)002:1380: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK060(i)002:1381: de bzhin nyid dang stong pa yi //
NK060(i)002:1382: yang dag nyid dang chos kyi dbyings //
NK060(i)002:1383: mtshan nyid med dang dmigs su med //
NK060(i)002:1384: bzung du med cing smon du med //
NK060(i)002:1385: ye nas mya ngan 'das pa yin //
NK060(i)002:1386: thams cad nam mkha'ii mtshan nyid de //
NK060(i)002:1387: nam mkha' la yang mtshan nyid med //
NK060(i)002:1390: med pa nyid na sna tshogs snang //
NK060(i)002:1391: thams cad shes rab dbyings las 'byung //
NK060(i)002:1394: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK060(i)002:1396: lhag pa don dam gyi gnas tshul sems nyid cir yang ma yin pas cir yang snang ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1397: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1398: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi gnas tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:1399: rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:1400: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa yang //
NK060(i)002:1401: 'dus byas dngos po sna tshogs ni //
NK060(i)002:1402: sgyu ma'i tshul du thams cad snang //
NK060(i)002:1403: 'bral snang bya ba kun byed kyang //
NK060(i)002:1404: rtog pa kun gyi tshad mar snang //
NK060(i)002:1405: 'di dag thams cad gzugs brnyan te //
NK060(i)002:1406: bya byed snang zhing dngos po med //
NK060(i)002:1407: chu zla'i tshul du thams cad gnas //
NK060(i)002:1408: thams cad snang la rang bzhin med //
NK060(i)002:1411: snang ba nyid na rang bzhin med //
NK060(i)002:1412: de nyid shes rab yin par bshad //
NK060(i)002:1413: rtag tu thabs nyid mi snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1416: gshegs sku sgyu mar snang ba dang //
NK060(i)002:1417: log rtog sgyu mar snang ba gnyis //
NK060(i)002:1418: yang dag log rtog khyad par bsam //
NK060(i)002:1419: sgyu ma yin phyir rang bzhin mnyam //
NK060(i)002:1420: zhes pa la sogs pa lhag pa kun rdzob chos
NK060(i)002:1421: thams cad rang rig sgyu mar snang ba tsam du
NK060(i)002:1423: dbyer med gnas tshul gyi don gong du bstan zin la/
NK060(i)002:1424: de dpes mtshon te bstan na/
NK060(i)002:1425: drag shul can gyis zhus pa'i mdo las/
NK060(i)002:1426: gser la bzo yi rnam pa ltar //
NK060(i)002:1427: snang ba dang po rang rig pas //
NK060(i)002:1430: gser la bzo'i rnam pa du mar byas kyang /
NK060(i)002:1431: ngo bo gser du dbyer med pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:1432: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas dbyer med du gnas so //
NK060(i)002:1433: de yang rgyas pa'i don drug pa las/
NK060(i)002:1434: chos rnams thams cad dbyer med gcig pa ste //
NK060(i)002:1435: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du'o //
NK060(i)002:1437: zhor la 'khrul tshul bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1438: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las/
NK060(i)002:1440: tshul dang nyes pa 'grub byed pa //
NK060(i)002:1441: nye bar mtshon pas rnam par dbye //
NK060(i)002:1442: zhor la spyi dgos bshad pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1443: zhes pas 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i tshul ni dgu las/
NK060(i)002:1444: dang po 'khrul pa'i rgyu la lnga ste/
NK060(i)002:1445: brgyud rgyu de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi gazhi'o //
NK060(i)002:1446: de yang 'di nyid kyi gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:1447: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK060(i)002:1449: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1451: sems rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba yin yang /
NK060(i)002:1452: nges pa'i shes pas nges par ma byas pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1453: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1455: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu kun tu btags pa'i rig
NK060(i)002:1456: pas 'gro ba rigs drug dang lhan cig byed pa'o
NK060(i)002:1457: // de yang 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1458: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK060(i)002:1460: nye bar len pa'i rgyu bag chags mthu can te/
NK060(i)002:1462: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs nas/
NK060(i)002:1465: rtog pa'i bag chags stug po yis //
NK060(i)002:1467: spyi'i rgyu bdag tu rtog pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1468: de yang 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1469: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK060(i)002:1471: gnyis pa'i 'khrul pa'i rkyen la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1474: dge ba'i las kyis mtho ris gnas bcu/
NK060(i)002:1475: sdig pa'i las kyis ngan song gnas bcu/
NK060(i)002:1476: mi g.yo ba'i las kyis khams gong ma gnyis su skye ba'i rkyen byed de/
NK060(i)002:1478: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK060(i)002:1481: zhe sdang gi rkyen gyis dmyal bar skye/
NK060(i)002:1485: phrag dog gis lha ma yin/
NK060(i)002:1486: nga rgyal gyis lhar skye ba'i rkyen byed de/
NK060(i)002:1487: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1488: thams cad mnyam par ma shes shing //
NK060(i)002:1489: ma lus kun la zhe sdang bas //
NK060(i)002:1490: snying rje yang dag med gyur na //
NK060(i)002:1491: 'di ni mi bzad chen po yin //
NK060(i)002:1492: dmyal khams bcu drug dag tu brgyud //
NK060(i)002:1493: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:1494: gsum pa 'khrul pa'i ngo bo'am 'bras bu ni/
NK060(i)002:1495: phyi nang snod bcud 'jig rten snang zhen gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad de/
NK060(i)002:1500: rgyud drug skye 'gag lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK060(i)002:1501: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK060(i)002:1504: thog ma med pa nas 'khor zhing 'khrul te/
NK060(i)002:1505: rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:1506: sems can khams gsum 'khor ba yi //
NK060(i)002:1507: thog ma med nas sems yan btang //
NK060(i)002:1510: rtsol med gzhi dus kun tu nyams //
NK060(i)002:1513: rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis kyis tshul du 'khor te/
NK060(i)002:1514: phyi rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis ni/
NK060(i)002:1515: rgyu dang 'brel pa drug /rkyen dang 'brel ba drug mang nyung gi tshul du 'khor/
NK060(i)002:1516: nang rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis ni/
NK060(i)002:1517: lus can rnams la dngos su 'khor la/
NK060(i)002:1518: lus med rnams la bag chags kyi tshul du 'khor te/
NK060(i)002:1519: de yang 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1522: drug pa 'khrul pa'i nyes pa ni gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1523: 'phags pa'i lam dang bral ba'i nyes pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1524: rgyas pa'i don ga sum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1525: sems can ma lus thams cad la //
NK060(i)002:1526: ye shes lnga yis kun khyab kyang //
NK060(i)002:1527: rang gi rnam rtog bsgribs byas nas //
NK060(i)002:1528: ye shes lnga yi don ma mthong //
NK060(i)002:1530: sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba'i nyes pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1532: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:1534: bdun pa 'khrul pa'i sgrub byed ni gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1537: ma bcos rgyun gyi skad cig ma //
NK060(i)002:1538: de yis ma byas gang yang med //
NK060(i)002:1540: bye brag 'khor ba sgrub par byed pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1541: log rtog rgyun gyi skad cig ma //
NK060(i)002:1542: de yis ma byas gang yang med //
NK060(i)002:1545: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK060(i)002:1547: brgyad pa 'khrul pa mtshon pa'i dpe ni gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1548: 'khor ba'i dpe zo chu'i khyud mo lta bu ni/
NK060(i)002:1549: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1550: r+ts+wa dang sog ma'i me bzhin du //
NK060(i)002:1551: khams gsum dbang du 'khor bar byed //
NK060(i)002:1554: r+ts+wa dang sog ma la me mched pa bzhin te/
NK060(i)002:1555: rtsa dang sog ma'i 'khor lo bzhin //
NK060(i)002:1556: long rtags rgyas shing brgyud par 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:1558: dgu pa zhor la la bzla ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1559: 'khor 'das rang bzhin dbyer med las ma g.yos pa ste/
NK060(i)002:1560: de yang rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1561: rnam par 'byang dang sdug bsngal dag /ye nas ngo bo yod min na //
NK060(i)002:1562: nyon mongs spang zhing bsgrub bya med //
NK060(i)002:1565: mchog gsum rdzogs pa man chod nas //
NK060(i)002:1566: ngan song gnas rnams thams cad kun //
NK060(i)002:1567: yang dag par ni dbyer med de //
NK060(i)002:1568: gang yang spar bar bya ba yin //
NK060(i)002:1571: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK060(i)002:1573: de lta bu'i gzhi de le'u'i gzhung las dngos bzung na/
NK060(i)002:1585: de ltar le'u bcu gcig gis shas tsam ston no //
NK060(i)002:1586: spyi don gnyis pa gdul bya lam gyi snang ba mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud dang /
NK060(i)002:1589: chos kyi dbyings ni kun la khyab pa yi //
NK060(i)002:1590: bla med theg pa bsam yas gsungs pa yang //
NK060(i)002:1591: so sor rang gi blo la snang bar zad //
NK060(i)002:1594: de bzhin nyid kyis ma bcos kyang //
NK060(i)002:1595: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK060(i)002:1596: zhes pas bstan pa blo dang 'tshams par snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1599: gzhi shes par bya pa la dgos te/
NK060(i)002:1601: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK060(i)002:1602: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK060(i)002:1604: 'bras bu thob par byed pa la dgos te/
NK060(i)002:1606: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK060(i)002:1607: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK060(i)002:1611: zhor la rgyud kyi nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:1613: rang bzhin 'bras bu rnam gnyis kyis //
NK060(i)002:1614: shes thob btags ming nges tshig gnyis //
NK060(i)002:1615: rgyu rkyen thabs 'brel dgos sogs phyir //
NK060(i)002:1616: rang gi nges tshig bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:1617: zhes pa la sogs pa'i nges tshig drug ste/
NK060(i)002:1618: gzhan las btags pa'i nges tshig gnyis ni/
NK060(i)002:1619: shes bya gzhi la rgyud du ming thob pas/
NK060(i)002:1620: de shes byed lam la yang rgyud du ming thob/
NK060(i)002:1621: thob bya 'bras bu la rgyud du ming thob pas/
NK060(i)002:1622: de thob byed lam la yang rgyud du ming thob bo //
NK060(i)002:1623: gang las thob pa'i nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:1627: dgos 'brel gdams gtad dang bzhi ni/
NK060(i)002:1628: rgyud don gyi nges tshig go //
NK060(i)002:1630: sems lnga skye'am skyes pa ste/
NK060(i)002:1632: rang bzhin mngon byed rnal 'byor pa //
NK060(i)002:1633: ngo bo rkyen gyis rnam par dbye //
NK060(i)002:1634: rigs dang rigs su nges pa yi //
NK060(i)002:1635: dang po rnam pa gnyis gyur pa //
NK060(i)002:1636: lnga sems ldan pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK060(i)002:1637: skye ba'i gzhi dang skye nges pa'o //
