NK060(i)002:1638: zhes pas spyir sems skye ba'i rgyu/
NK060(i)002:1641: skyes pa'i ngo bo rnams rim par dbye ru rung mod/
NK060(i)002:1642: 'on kyang lam gyi ngo bo la dbye na 'dod lugs mang ste/
NK060(i)002:1644: kun kyang smin zin bgrod pa med //
NK060(i)002:1645: de nyid lam gyi ngo bo ste/
NK060(i)002:1647: bgrod bya'i ngos nas lam gyi ngo bor bzhag /rim gsum las/
NK060(i)002:1648: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum ste //
NK060(i)002:1649: sems lnga skyes par bstan pa yin //
NK060(i)002:1651: bgrod tshul gyi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bor bzhag /mdo don bsdus kyi/
NK060(i)002:1652: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK060(i)002:1654: rnam grangs kyi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bor bzhag ste/
NK060(i)002:1656: ngo bo sems lnga skyes pa dang //
NK060(i)002:1659: 'jig ldang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK060(i)002:1660: nges par skye ba'i ngo bor 'dod //
NK060(i)002:1662: lam gyi ngo bo sems lnga la bzhag ste/
NK060(i)002:1664: thun mong sems lnga ni sbyangs pa'i dbang po rnon po'i skabs su skye bas zhor la bshad do //
NK060(i)002:1665: skabs 'dir mchog gi sems lnga la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1666: grol lam gyi sems lnga ni/
NK060(i)002:1667: skye bo dang mu stegs theg pa 'og ma rnams kyi zhe 'dod las grol nas/
NK060(i)002:1668: gsang sngags su 'go g.yo ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1669: g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK060(i)002:1670: zhi bde dbyer med kyi don khong du chud par
NK060(i)002:1671: smon pa ni smon pa byang chub kyi sems dang
NK060(i)002:1672: / dbyer med kyi don la 'jug pa ni 'jug pa'i sems dang /
NK060(i)002:1673: zhugs nas dbyer med kyi don la gnas pa ni gnas pa'i sems dang /
NK060(i)002:1674: gnas pas lam lnga mthar phyin pa mthar phyin pa'i sems skye ba'o //
NK060(i)002:1675: thabs lam gyi sems lnga ni/
NK060(i)002:1677: 'jig dang ldang dang gnas pa dang //
NK060(i)002:1678: smon pa byang chub sems yin no //
NK060(i)002:1679: g.yo dang skyed dang ldang dang gnas //
NK060(i)002:1681: g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems ni/
NK060(i)002:1682: lam pas thabs lam nyams su len pa'i dus su/
NK060(i)002:1683: rtsa gnas nas thig le 'go g.yo tsam na/
NK060(i)002:1684: bde ba 'go ldang ba'i tshul du 'dug pas na g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)002:1685: bde ba snga ma 'jig cing phyi ma la 'jug pa ni 'jig 'jug byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)002:1686: lus rtsa dang thig le rnams rang sar gnas pas/
NK060(i)002:1687: bde ba yang rang sar gnas pa ni gnas pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)002:1688: snga ma'i bde ba la dmigs shing phyi ma'i bde
NK060(i)002:1689: ba la smon pa ni smon pa byang chub kyi
NK060(i)002:1690: sems so // thig le rdo rje'i rtse mo nas phar 'gro ba dang /
NK060(i)002:1691: pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru nas tshur 'ong ba ni 'gro 'ong byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)002:1692: 'o na lam gyi ngo bo sems lnga yin na/
NK060(i)002:1693: lam pa gang gis byed ce na/
NK060(i)002:1694: sems lnga skye ba'i gzhi ma'i ngos nas lam pa yin la/
NK060(i)002:1695: skyes pa rang gi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bo yin no //
NK060(i)002:1696: 'o na cig car ba'i rten gyi gang zag la sems lnga rim gyi skye'am cig car skye/
NK060(i)002:1697: snga ma ltar na cig car ba yin pa dang 'gal/
NK060(i)002:1698: phyi ma ltar na g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems skyes pa'i tshe na/
NK060(i)002:1699: mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems skye'am mi skye/
NK060(i)002:1700: skye na bar gyi sems gsum la dgos pa med par 'gyur/
NK060(i)002:1701: mi skye na rim gyis pa dang khyad med par 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)002:1702: 'di la bla ma gong ma rnams kyi bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)002:1703: sems lnga myur bar skye ba la cig car ba dang /
NK060(i)002:1704: bul bar skye ba la rim gyis par gsungs te/
NK060(i)002:1706: rta mgyogs par rgyug pa dang bul bar rgyug pa lta bu'am/
NK060(i)002:1707: sho mang 'dab ma lnga sbrags la lag myur pos khab gtsag byed pa dang /
NK060(i)002:1708: shing leb lnga sbrags la gsor gyis 'bugs pa lta bu yin gsung /
NK060(i)002:1709: rgya gab gong pa'i bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)002:1710: rten gyi gang zag blo che ba la sems lnga cig car du skye la/
NK060(i)002:1711: skye lugs ni sems lnga'i ngo bo dbyer med du skye ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:1712: de yang sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las/
NK060(i)002:1713: lhun gyis rtogs nas lhun gyis bsgom //
NK060(i)002:1715: skabs kyis rdzogs pa chen por brjod //
NK060(i)002:1717: bzhi pa don gyi dmigs bzung nas rnam grangs rnam par phye na/
NK060(i)002:1718: blo che chung gi sgo nas rim dang cig car gnyis su dbye/
NK060(i)002:1719: mtshan ma che chung gi sgo nas lha dang rtog pa gnyis su dbye/
NK060(i)002:1720: gdul bya 'drag zhan gyi sgo nas zhi khro gnyis su dbye/
NK060(i)002:1721: rim pa 'dor mi 'dor gyi sgo nas thod brgal mthar chags gnyis su dbye ste/
NK060(i)002:1722: da res sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho dang /
NK060(i)002:1723: 'di nyid kyi le'u bdun pa'i rjes su 'brang nas
NK060(i)002:1724: chags pa'i che chung gi sgo nas thabs lam grol
NK060(i)002:1727: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK060(i)002:1730: gzhi dang skabs kyi skye 'gyur pa //
NK060(i)002:1731: grol lam thabs su rnam par bshad //
NK060(i)002:1733: thabs lam ni thabs kyi man ngag dang ldan pas
NK060(i)002:1734: nyon mongs pa la spyad kyang mi 'ching zhing grol
NK060(i)002:1735: ba ste/ 'di nyid kyi bcu pa las/
NK060(i)002:1736: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK060(i)002:1737: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK060(i)002:1741: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin byang chub sems sogs rgyu 'khor lo //
NK060(i)002:1742: 'bras bu rgyal ba smin grub ngo mtshar ming tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK060(i)002:1745: chos nyid kyi don la shes rab rnams pa gsum gyis sbyor ba ste/
NK060(i)002:1746: 'di nyid kyi bcu gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1747: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK060(i)002:1748: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK060(i)002:1749: rang byung sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK060(i)002:1751: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1752: de bas thos bsam sgom pa yis //
NK060(i)002:1753: yang dag don nyid rtogs bya ste //
NK060(i)002:1755: de la dang po thabs lam la'ang rim cig car gnyis las/
NK060(i)002:1756: rim gyis pa ni steng sgo 'khor lo 'ju 'dul
NK060(i)002:1757: gyi man ngag nyams su blangs pas bde ba'i ye
NK060(i)002:1758: shes rim gyis skye ba ste/
NK060(i)002:1760: 'khor lo bzhi dang srog shing gsum //
NK060(i)002:1761: me rlung 'gro ba nam mkha'i ba //
NK060(i)002:1762: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK060(i)002:1766: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:1767: thar lam cig car ba ni/
NK060(i)002:1768: 'og sgo zab mo'i dbang gsum gyi man ngag nyams
NK060(i)002:1769: su blangs pas bde ba'i ye shes cig car du
NK060(i)002:1770: skye ba ste/ de yang khams nyer gcig pa las/
NK060(i)002:1771: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK060(i)002:1772: phun sum tshogs pa'i lhun grub rnams //
NK060(i)002:1773: gsang dbang mchog gis sbyin par byed //
NK060(i)002:1775: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:1776: cig car dbang lnga rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK060(i)002:1777: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK060(i)002:1778: 'o na thabs kyi lam de dag gsal bar ston pa'i gzhung gang la ngos 'dzin zhe na/
NK060(i)002:1783: bcu gsum pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:1784: gnyis pa grol lam la yang rim dang cig car gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1786: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad pa gyis //
NK060(i)002:1787: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK060(i)002:1790: blo yi shes rab che chung gis //
NK060(i)002:1791: yang na cig car bsgom par bya //
NK060(i)002:1793: 'o na de gnyis kyi khyad par gang zhe na/
NK060(i)002:1794: lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus su/
NK060(i)002:1795: rim gyis gtan la phab nas/
NK060(i)002:1796: sgom pas nyams su len pa'i dus su bden pa kha phral nas bsgom/
NK060(i)002:1797: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dus su rim gyis mthar phyin par byed pa zhig rim gyis so //
NK060(i)002:1799: lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus su dbyer med cig chod du rtogs/
NK060(i)002:1800: sgom pas nyams su len pa'i dus su dbyer med gcig chod du bsgom/
NK060(i)002:1801: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dus su dbyer med cig
NK060(i)002:1802: chod du phyin par byed pa zhig cig car ba'o
NK060(i)002:1803: // yang na rtogs goms rim gyis mthar phyin pa rim gyis/
NK060(i)002:1804: rtogs goms thams cad cig chod du mthar phyin pa cig car ro //
NK060(i)002:1805: de gnyis kar yang mtshan nyid gsum dang sbyor ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:1806: 'di nyid kyi bcu gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)002:1808: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK060(i)002:1809: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK060(i)002:1810: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK060(i)002:1813: mtshan nyid gsum gyis don mthar phyin par byed do //
NK060(i)002:1815: de yang brjod bya nyung bas cig car ba thog mar bshad na/
NK060(i)002:1816: rtogs goms dus gcig la mthar phyin pas cig car ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:1818: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK060(i)002:1819: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK060(i)002:1820: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob 'gyur bas //
NK060(i)002:1823: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin las //
NK060(i)002:1824: bsgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:1825: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK060(i)002:1826: de ni kun tu snang gi dang //
NK060(i)002:1827: de ni rgyu yi rim par bstan //
NK060(i)002:1830: ma bcos ji bzhin ngang bzhag nas //
NK060(i)002:1834: lhun gyis grub nas lhun gyis bsgom //
NK060(i)002:1835: rim bral de nyid gsal gyur 'brel //
NK060(i)002:1836: skabs kyi rdzogs pa chen por brjod //
NK060(i)002:1838: grol lam cig car bde dag gsal bar/
NK060(i)002:1843: bcu dgu pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:1844: grol lam rim gyis pa rtogs goms rim gyis mthar phyin par byed pa la/
NK060(i)002:1845: lam gyi bye brag bzhir phye na/
NK060(i)002:1846: zag pa med la ldog pa yod pa'i lam pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1847: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i rten gyi gang zag gang
NK060(i)002:1848: zhig /theg chen gyi tshogs sbyor gyi lam la gnas
NK060(i)002:1849: pa de'o // zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i lam pa tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi'o //
NK060(i)002:1850: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i lam pa/
NK060(i)002:1851: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK060(i)002:1852: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam pa/
NK060(i)002:1853: mthong lam rnam pa gnyis yan chod do //
NK060(i)002:1854: de la zag pa ni chos mngon pa las/
NK060(i)002:1855: zag pa'i sgo drug tu bshad kyang /
NK060(i)002:1856: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba/
NK060(i)002:1859: lus/ khams/ skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum du bzhed do //
NK060(i)002:1860: ldog pa ni lam phyir ldog pa ste/
NK060(i)002:1861: 'di ni srid pa la dgongs kyis khyab pa ni med do //
NK060(i)002:1863: skabs 'dir man ngag lta phreng rjes su 'brangs nas mtshan nyid gsum du 'chad de/
NK060(i)002:1864: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba/
NK060(i)002:1865: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin/
NK060(i)002:1866: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid dang gsum las/
NK060(i)002:1868: lta ba rtogs pa gdams pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1870: gang gis dmigs med mi shes pa //
NK060(i)002:1871: de yis chos kyi dbyings mi shes //
NK060(i)002:1872: de phyir dngos dang dngos med pas //
NK060(i)002:1873: 'jig pas dmigs med shes par gyis //
NK060(i)002:1875: lta ba rang gi ngo bo ni/
NK060(i)002:1876: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK060(i)002:1877: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK060(i)002:1878: mtshan med ma yin rig brgyud min //
NK060(i)002:1879: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK060(i)002:1880: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK060(i)002:1881: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK060(i)002:1882: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK060(i)002:1884: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la lnga ste/
NK060(i)002:1885: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ni/
NK060(i)002:1887: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pas //
NK060(i)002:1888: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK060(i)002:1889: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK060(i)002:1890: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK060(i)002:1892: snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor ni/
NK060(i)002:1893: de bzhin nyid la spros med kyang //
NK060(i)002:1894: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK060(i)002:1895: sems can rnams la snying rje'i phyir //
NK060(i)002:1896: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK060(i)002:1898: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor la phra rags gnyis las/
NK060(i)002:1899: phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1900: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK060(i)002:1901: yi ge'i yid bzhin rin cen sprin //
NK060(i)002:1904: phyi nang snod bcud h+aum du bsdu //
NK060(i)002:1906: rags pa lha sku la bslab pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1907: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1908: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud pa bcas //
NK060(i)002:1909: gru chad bzhis brgyan bar khyams dang //
NK060(i)002:1910: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK060(i)002:1911: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK060(i)002:1912: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK060(i)002:1913: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK060(i)002:1914: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK060(i)002:1915: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK060(i)002:1916: zhes pa zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang dang /
NK060(i)002:1917: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK060(i)002:1918: phyogs bcu rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK060(i)002:1920: gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan //
NK060(i)002:1921: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK060(i)002:1922: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK060(i)002:1923: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi mas brjid //
NK060(i)002:1924: 'bar ba'i 'phro ba mang po 'khrug /khyu mchog ma
NK060(i)002:1925: he gzig dang stag /gtum pa dom gyi sbar bas
NK060(i)002:1926: ni // dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK060(i)002:1927: zhes khro bo'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK060(i)002:1928: brten pa lha sgom pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1929: de bzhin gnyis med gsal gyur nas //
NK060(i)002:1930: sku gcig rdo rje dril 'bar sgom //
NK060(i)002:1932: mkha' dkyil dwangs pa'i dbyings nyi zla //
NK060(i)002:1933: ye shes rgyal po stangs dpyal bsgom //
NK060(i)002:1935: phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i rnal 'byor ni/
NK060(i)002:1936: zhi khro'i lha tshogs dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum dang /
NK060(i)002:1939: rtsa ba yan lag lhag pa'i lha dang bcas pa bsgom ste/
NK060(i)002:1940: de yang rnam grangs kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)002:1941: sgyu 'phrul 'bring po'i lha tshogs tshom bu stong dang /
NK060(i)002:1943: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la sogs
NK060(i)002:1944: pa rnam par snang byed kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK060(i)002:1946: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK060(i)002:1947: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste //
NK060(i)002:1949: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK060(i)002:1950: rgyal ba rgyal mchog ji bzhin du //
NK060(i)002:1953: de bzhin du dkyil 'khor 'khor dang tshom bu'i lha tshogs thams cad la shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:1954: de rnams ni tshogs kyi lam mo //
NK060(i)002:1955: bar chad med pa'i lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa la zhi khro gnyis las/
NK060(i)002:1960: 'di nyid kyi bcu gcig pa las/
NK060(i)002:1961: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK060(i)002:1962: thugs kyi thugs te thug kyi mchog /ces so //
NK060(i)002:1964: de bzhin rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK060(i)002:1965: pad+ma'i rigs te sku gsung thugs //
NK060(i)002:1966: khro bo'i tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK060(i)002:1967: tshom bu gsum pa'i lha rnams bsgom //
NK060(i)002:1970: lnga dang lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK060(i)002:1971: tshom bu lnga yi lha rnams bsgom //
NK060(i)002:1973: khro bo'i tshogs sgrub pa ni/
NK060(i)002:1974: pho nya phyag brnyan bka' nyan tshogs //
NK060(i)002:1975: ci bgyi la sogs tshogs rnams kyis //
NK060(i)002:1976: dngos grub las rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK060(i)002:1978: de dag ni sbyor ba'i lam mo //
NK060(i)002:1979: gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:1980: gnas skabs lam 'gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK060(i)002:1981: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu sku lnga'o //
NK060(i)002:1982: de la rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)002:1983: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gnyis ni/
NK060(i)002:1986: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK060(i)002:1989: gsang ba'i yo byad lnga ldan pas //
NK060(i)002:1990: brtson pas tshul bzhin rab bsgrubs na //
NK060(i)002:1991: rdo rje'i lus dang rnam smin du //
NK060(i)002:1995: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK060(i)002:1997: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'dzin ni sgom lam pa yin te/
NK060(i)002:1999: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK060(i)002:2000: bsgom pa mngon du 'gyur ba'i lha //
NK060(i)002:2001: mngon shes drug dang mtshan bzang pos //
NK060(i)002:2002: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs su grags //
NK060(i)002:2004: 'di nyid kyi bcu gcig pa las kyang /
NK060(i)002:2005: gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK060(i)002:2007: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin ni/
NK060(i)002:2008: mthar phyin pa'i lam pa yin te/
NK060(i)002:2010: rang rig ye shes rgyud don phyir //
NK060(i)002:2011: rang gi rig pa mngon byas pas //
NK060(i)002:2012: rig 'dzin mchog kyang lhun grub pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2023: bcu gsum pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:2024: zhor la mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud kyi bshad thabs la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2025: rgyud gzhung ngos bzung ba dang /
NK060(i)002:2029: thabs dang shes rab ma ning rgyud //
NK060(i)002:2030: bstan pa'i rgyud lam rkyen du 'dod //
NK060(i)002:2032: spyir gyi rgyud la gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:2033: lha yab dang lam steng sgo gtso bor ston pa
NK060(i)002:2034: gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa thabs pha'i rgyud
NK060(i)002:2035: dang / lha yum dang lam 'og sgo gtso bor
NK060(i)002:2036: ston pa bde mchog 'khor lo la sogs pa shes
NK060(i)002:2038: lha yab yum 'go mnyam dang lam steng 'og kha
NK060(i)002:2039: sbyor gtso bor ston pa sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor la
NK060(i)002:2041: thabs shes gnyis med kyi rgyud do //
NK060(i)002:2042: 'dir gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud 'di ni/
NK060(i)002:2043: rgyud sde mtha' dag gi 'byung khungs kyang yin la
NK060(i)002:2044: gtan la dbab bya'ang yin pa'i phyir kun gyi spyi
NK060(i)002:2045: rgyud yin te/ 'di nyid kyi tha ma las/
NK060(i)002:2046: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi/
NK060(i)002:2049: lung gi spyi ni shin tu zab pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)002:2050: khams nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bstan ces pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2052: lung gi spyi ru grags pa ni //
NK060(i)002:2053: rnam par dbye bas lnga ru 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:2055: spyi rgyud du ngos bzung ngo //
NK060(i)002:2056: gnyis pa de bshad pa'i thabs ni/
NK060(i)002:2058: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK060(i)002:2059: mthun par gsang bsgrags gzhan du min //
NK060(i)002:2062: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK060(i)002:2063: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK060(i)002:2064: gzhon nus rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK060(i)002:2065: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK060(i)002:2068: rab la mtshan bstan pas go ba/
NK060(i)002:2070: sman 'tsho byed gzhon nus lag gi rtsa la bltas pas/
NK060(i)002:2071: lus mgo 'jug gi nad rtogs pa lta bu'o //
NK060(i)002:2072: 'bring la spyi don rnam par phye bas rtogs pa sman snod kyi kha byang lta bu'o //
NK060(i)002:2073: tha ma 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas bsnyad pas rtogs pas/
NK060(i)002:2074: sman re re yang dbyibs kha dog ro nus bzhu
NK060(i)002:2075: rjes 'dra dpe rnams kyis gtan la 'bebs pa lta
NK060(i)002:2076: bu'o // de la dang po mtshan bstan pa yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2078: dbang po rab kyis mtshan mthong ba'am thos pa tsam
NK060(i)002:2079: gyis rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don khong du chud pa
NK060(i)002:2080: dang / 'bring gis don mdo tsam rtogs pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2081: tha mas kyang rgyud gzhung 'di ni 'di skad bya
NK060(i)002:2082: ba yin par 'dug snyam du myur du ngos zin
NK060(i)002:2083: par bya ba'i dgos pa yod/
NK060(i)002:2085: don mtshon par byed pa'i bla dwags yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2087: rgyud kyi don rtogs dka' ba bcud 'dus pa gzhan
NK060(i)002:2088: sel ba nges don the tshom dang bral ba rnams
NK060(i)002:2089: mtshon pa'i ming gi rnam grangs zhig yin no //
NK060(i)002:2090: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2091: spyir gyi gdul bya sna tshogs pa'i bsam pa la dgongs nas/
NK060(i)002:2092: yul dang dus dang gnas la sogs pa'i dbang gis/
NK060(i)002:2093: mtshan gyi rnam grangs sgyu 'phrul snying po dang /
NK060(i)002:2095: 'phags pa rtogs pa'i rgyal po la sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK060(i)002:2096: khyad par du don la mtshan du btags pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2097: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud yin no //
NK060(i)002:2098: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2100: lung gi spyi ru grags pa ni //
NK060(i)002:2101: rnam par dbye bas lnga ru 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:2104: rgyud kyi rgyu dang rkyen dang yongs su shes par bya ba dang /
NK060(i)002:2106: yongs su gtad pa'o zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2108: rgyud gzhung gzhi bslang yongs su shes //
NK060(i)002:2109: dgos 'brel gtad pa yongs su rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:2113: yongs su shes par bya ba dngos po rgyud kyi don/
NK060(i)002:2115: dang po gleng gzhi la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2117: gleng gzhi tshogs pas bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu byed pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2118: gleng gzhi tshogs lugs kyi lo rgyus la brten nas
NK060(i)002:2119: rjes 'jug gi lam pa yid ches shing 'jug pa'i
NK060(i)002:2120: dgos pa yod/ nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:2121: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu'ang gzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2123: phun sum tshogs pa drug ldan zhig yin/
NK060(i)002:2124: rnam grangs rnam par phye na bzhi ste/
NK060(i)002:2125: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi/
NK060(i)002:2126: rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi/
NK060(i)002:2127: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi/
NK060(i)002:2128: gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK060(i)002:2130: sngags kyi rgyud yo ga man chad kyi spyod yul ma yin te/
NK060(i)002:2135: gnas snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo/
NK060(i)002:2136: ston pa srog mi shigs pa'i thig le yi ge bam gyi dbyibs can/
NK060(i)002:2137: 'khor rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad kyi rtogs pa/
NK060(i)002:2138: bstan pa don dam byang chub kyi sems ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can no //
NK060(i)002:2139: dus snga phyi'i rtog pa dang bral te bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK060(i)002:2140: sdud pa po tshogs bdun kun gyis rjes su 'jug pa'i yid kyi rnam shes so //
NK060(i)002:2142: gnas yum gyi b+ha ga /ston pa gsang ba'i rdo rje/
NK060(i)002:2143: 'khor bde ba sdom par byed pa'i yid la sogs pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rtog pa/
NK060(i)002:2144: bstan pa dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha'i skad cig
NK060(i)002:2145: ma rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes so
NK060(i)002:2146: // dus ston pa gsang ba'i sku gtsug tor 'khor lo sgyur ba'i dus so //
NK060(i)002:2147: sdud pa po bde ba sdom par byed pa'i yid do //
NK060(i)002:2151: zhes pa'i 'di skabs 'dir thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi dbang btsan du byas na/
NK060(i)002:2152: sngon kyi lo ts+aa ba mkhas pa rnams kyis 'di
NK060(i)002:2153: skad bshad pa'i dus na zhes bsgyur ba yin no
NK060(i)002:2154: // de las gzhan du 'di skad thos su bsgyur ba rnams ni/
NK060(i)002:2155: thun mong gi gleng gzhi mdor bstan yin par rig par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:2156: gnyis pa rgyud khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi ni/
NK060(i)002:2157: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi yin te/
NK060(i)002:2159: ston pa ni drug pa spyi'i gzugs can no //
NK060(i)002:2160: 'khor ni dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor rigs lnga yab yum/
NK060(i)002:2161: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor sems dpa' sems ma/
NK060(i)002:2162: 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor khro bo dang khro mo rnams so //
NK060(i)002:2163: bstan pa ni rgyud gzhung 'di nyid do //
NK060(i)002:2165: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor gyi nang nas phyag na rdo rjes bsdus so //
NK060(i)002:2167: rgyud 'di nyid kyi le'u dang pos ston no //
NK060(i)002:2168: gsum pa bstan pa 'byung ba'i spyi'i gleng gzhi ni/
NK060(i)002:2169: gnas phyogs bcu'i zhing khams mtha' yas pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2170: ston pa thub pa drug go //
NK060(i)002:2172: bstan pa 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun pa'i chos ston pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2173: dus ni ston 'khor gnas gsum nam 'dzom pa'i dus so //
NK060(i)002:2175: rgyud 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa'i stod kyi ston no //
NK060(i)002:2176: bzhi pa gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gzhi ni/
NK060(i)002:2177: gnas bzod par dka' ba'i dur khrod chen po/
NK060(i)002:2178: ston pa dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka /'khor ru tra 'khor dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)002:2180: dus gdul bya skabs la babs pa'i dus so //
NK060(i)002:2182: rgyud 'di'i le'u bco lnga pas ston no //
NK060(i)002:2183: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2185: bstan pa myur du 'byung ba'i dgos ched yod do //
NK060(i)002:2187: dris lan la brten nas bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2190: rnam grangs rnam par dbye na gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:2191: ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang ba dang /
NK060(i)002:2192: 'khor gyis gus pas dri ba dris te gleng bslang ba dang /
NK060(i)002:2193: skabs la gleng du bslang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2194: spyir gyis gleng bslang lugs de ltar yin kyang /
NK060(i)002:2195: skabs 'dir ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2196: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang yin te/
NK060(i)002:2197: lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams la don dam nges pa'i
NK060(i)002:2198: tshig gis rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don ngos
NK060(i)002:2200: 'khor gyis gus pas bri ba dris te gleng bslang ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2201: thun mong gi gleng bslang ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:2202: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du thun mong gi
NK060(i)002:2203: bstan pa dang theg pa gsung bar zhus pa'i lan
NK060(i)002:2204: du/ lam steng kyi ston pa thub pa drug spro bar zhal gyis bzhes nas/
NK060(i)002:2205: bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig gis rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don brgyud nas ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2206: de bzhin du skabs la gleng gleng du bslang ba
NK060(i)002:2207: yang thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i bye
NK060(i)002:2210: 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa'i stod du zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba bstan nas/
NK060(i)002:2211: smad du bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen gleng bslang ston no //
NK060(i)002:2212: gsum pa yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud kyi don la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2214: lam pas nyams su blangs pas rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK060(i)002:2215: snying po'i don khong du chud par 'gyur ba'i dgos
NK060(i)002:2216: ched yod do // nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:2217: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyang mtshon bya don gyi rgyud kyi shes byed yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2218: ngo bo dang dmigs bzung thun mong du bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2219: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam dang //
NK060(i)002:2220: mchod sngags ting 'dzin phrin sgrub kyis //
NK060(i)002:2221: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK060(i)002:2223: rgyud don yongs su shes byed kyi dngos po bcu ru gsungs te/
NK060(i)002:2225: de kho na nyid lta ba/
NK060(i)002:2229: mi 'da' ba dam tshig /rol pa phrin las/
NK060(i)002:2230: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa/
NK060(i)002:2232: gnas su stob pa mchod pa/
NK060(i)002:2233: 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag rgya dang bcu las/
NK060(i)002:2234: dang po lta ba la bzhi ste/
NK060(i)002:2236: nges tshig /ngo bo rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba/
NK060(i)002:2237: zhor la lta ba ma rtogs pa dang rtogs pa'i skyon yon bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2241: dang po gzhan sel ni le'u bcu gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:2242: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK060(i)002:2243: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK060(i)002:2246: rgyang 'phen log par rtogs pa rtag pa dang chad pa/
NK060(i)002:2247: phyogs rtogs nyan thos dang rang rgyal/
NK060(i)002:2248: yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa dbu ma dang sems tsam ste/
NK060(i)002:2249: de rnams kyi lta ba sel lo //
NK060(i)002:2251: chos nyid zab mo'i don la blo 'byor ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK060(i)002:2252: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal la ji mi snyam pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK060(i)002:2253: 'bras bu ma btsal ba lhun gyis grub pa'i dgos ched yod do //
NK060(i)002:2255: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:2256: chos kyi rang bzhin ji lta bu //
NK060(i)002:2257: bdag gis yang dag rtogs bya ste //
NK060(i)002:2260: thabs dang shes rab rtogs pa yi //
NK060(i)002:2261: dug gsum sdug bsngal gnod mi 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:2264: yang dag ye shes rab rtogs na //
NK060(i)002:2265: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK060(i)002:2268: sems nyid dngos po'i gshis dang mi 'gal bar rjes su rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2270: lta dang blta bar byar med pas //
NK060(i)002:2271: ye shes sgron ma bsgrengs pas ni //
NK060(i)002:2272: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK060(i)002:2274: ngo bo dang rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don
NK060(i)002:2275: gyi dmigs bzung ba thun mong du bstan pa la
NK060(i)002:2276: gsum ste/ gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste don gyi dmigs bzung /
NK060(i)002:2277: gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad de don gyi dmigs bzung /
NK060(i)002:2278: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2279: dang po gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab pa la gsum las gzhal bya ni/
NK060(i)002:2285: mnyam pa gnyis sam bzhi ste/
NK060(i)002:2286: dang po ni 'di nyid kyi bcu gcig pa las/
NK060(i)002:2287: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK060(i)002:2288: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK060(i)002:2289: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK060(i)002:2290: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK060(i)002:2293: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK060(i)002:2296: mnyam nyid lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK060(i)002:2298: gtan tshigs de dag gis gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' ni/
NK060(i)002:2299: bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba zhig yin te/
NK060(i)002:2300: de yang don dam pa'i bden pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2301: mtha' gang du yang ma red pa'i sems nyid ye
NK060(i)002:2302: nas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dbyings dang
NK060(i)002:2303: ye shes kyi ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa ste/
NK060(i)002:2304: don dam du ni dkor bdun no //
NK060(i)002:2306: de nyid kyi rtsal snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:2307: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK060(i)002:2309: de dag mtshon byed kyi tshig la snga phyi byung yang /
NK060(i)002:2310: mtshon bya'i don mnyam pa nyid du gnas te/
NK060(i)002:2311: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yi //
NK060(i)002:2312: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK060(i)002:2313: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK060(i)002:2316: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK060(i)002:2317: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan med de //
NK060(i)002:2318: rnam dag dbyings nyid tshul gcig go //
NK060(i)002:2321: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba
NK060(i)002:2322: thams cad kyi gol sa dang sgrib pa ngos bzung
NK060(i)002:2323: nas/ mthar thug mnyam pa nyid du la zlos par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2324: de yang rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:2325: kun khyab mnyam pa nyid yin pas //
NK060(i)002:2327: so so'i lta ba brjod mi lang //
NK060(i)002:2329: gsum pa rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba la gnyis/
NK060(i)002:2333: shes rab kyi tshogs brgyad de //
NK060(i)002:2334: shes dang spyod yul gnyis med pas //
NK060(i)002:2335: thams cad ma lus gcig gi ngang //
NK060(i)002:2336: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal stong gzugs //
NK060(i)002:2337: lta dang blta bar byar med par //
NK060(i)002:2338: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK060(i)002:2339: gang du'ang ma mthong spyan gyi mchog /ces pas/
NK060(i)002:2340: don mthong ba ni shes rab spyan gyi lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2341: khyab gsal rang rig go ba'i sgra //
NK060(i)002:2342: thos pa med par thos pa yi //
NK060(i)002:2344: don thos pa shes rab snyan gyi lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2345: dang bas tshim byed chos kyi dri //
NK060(i)002:2346: sgom byed med par tshor ba'i shangs //
NK060(i)002:2348: don tsher ba shes rab spangs kyi lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2349: myong ba'i bya byed gnyis med myong //
NK060(i)002:2351: nyams su myong ba shes rab ljags kyi lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2352: yang dag don la reg pa nyid //
NK060(i)002:2353: reg pa kun dngos reg dang bral //
NK060(i)002:2355: shes rab lus kyi lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2356: chos khams sna tshogs kun mkhyen pa //
NK060(i)002:2357: rang rig rgyal po rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2359: bdag nyid chen por rtogs pa shes rab yid kyi lta ba/
NK060(i)002:2360: de bas bdag 'dzin rang gsal ba //
NK060(i)002:2361: bdag ces bdag dang bral ba'i yid //
NK060(i)002:2363: thams cad rang snang rang gsal ba shes rab nyon yid kyi lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2364: don dang sems rtogs med gsal ba //
NK060(i)002:2365: rang byung ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NK060(i)002:2367: don sems rtog med du gsal ba shes rab kun gzhi'i lta ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2368: don gyi rnam grangs la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2369: lam gyi rim pa'i lta grangs dgu dang /
NK060(i)002:2370: rgyud don gyi lta grangs dagu'o //
NK060(i)002:2372: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK060(i)002:2373: rang rig ye shes snying rjes gzigs //
NK060(i)002:2374: phyag rgya gcig sku 'bras bur lta //
NK060(i)002:2375: thams cad gsal ba'i lta ba dang //
NK060(i)002:2376: bar chad med pa'i tshogs chen mthong //
NK060(i)002:2377: dbang sgyur mnyam nyid mi g.yo ba //
NK060(i)002:2378: ye shes kun mkhyen lta ba dgu //
NK060(i)002:2380: rgyud don gyi lta grangs dgu ni/
NK060(i)002:2382: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK060(i)002:2383: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK060(i)002:2384: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK060(i)002:2386: dam tshig bsrung bya srung byed dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2387: spyod par byed dang spyad med pa //
NK060(i)002:2388: spyod byed med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK060(i)002:2389: kun la thogs pa med par spyad //
NK060(i)002:2391: spyad bya spyod byed dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2392: bzhi yi las dang gcig pu yang //
NK060(i)002:2393: thig le chen po'i ngang du nges //
NK060(i)002:2395: phrin las bzhi'i ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2396: mchod pa'i rgyan dang longs spyod kun //
NK060(i)002:2397: rang rig byang chub sems chen po //
NK060(i)002:2398: phul ba med par thams cad mnyes //
NK060(i)002:2400: mchod pa dbul bya 'bul byed dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2401: gzhal yas khang dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK060(i)002:2403: sems kyi cho 'phrul chen po yin //
NK060(i)002:2404: de bas rnam mkhyen rig pa'i ngang //
NK060(i)002:2406: dkyil 'khor rang rig tu rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2407: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK060(i)002:2408: dbang lnga ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:2409: bco brgyad rang rig cho 'phrul snang //
NK060(i)002:2411: dbang rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul du rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2412: e ma ma sgrub sgrub chen po //
NK060(i)002:2413: sgrub pa chen po ye shes che //
NK060(i)002:2415: bsnyen sgrub bzhi rang rig tu rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2416: ting 'dzin lta ba'i bye brag kun //
NK060(i)002:2417: rang rig snang byed chu bur dang //
NK060(i)002:2418: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin pas //
NK060(i)002:2420: ting 'dzin chu bur ram nam mkha' lta bur rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2421: sngags dang phyag rgya sems nyid phyir //
NK060(i)002:2422: brag ca chu zla 'drar byas nas //
NK060(i)002:2424: sngags dang phyag rgya chu zla'am brag ca lta bur shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:2425: zhor la ma rtogs pa'i rkyen la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2426: sangs rgyas kyi zhing ngan song gi gnas su mthong ba'i skyon ni/
NK060(i)002:2428: yang dag rtogs pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK060(i)002:2429: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK060(i)002:2431: dge ba'i las spyad kyang 'khor ba las ma grol ba'i skyon ni/
NK060(i)002:2432: thabs la mkhas pas ma zin na //
NK060(i)002:2433: lam gyi dge spyad stegs spyad kyang //
NK060(i)002:2434: skye shi med pa'i sa mi thob //
NK060(i)002:2436: rtogs pa'i yon tan la gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:2437: ngan song gi gnas kyang sangs rgyas kyi zhing du mthong ba'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)002:2438: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pas na //
NK060(i)002:2439: ngan song gnas kyang bde gshegs zhing du mthong //
NK060(i)002:2441: nyon mongs pa ci spyad kyang mi 'ching ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2442: 'di nyid kyi bcu dgu pa las/
NK060(i)002:2443: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK060(i)002:2444: nyon mongs las rnams ci spyad kyang //
NK060(i)002:2445: byas la mi sogs tshogs 'gyur te //
NK060(i)002:2446: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK060(i)002:2448: 'khor bar mi ldog cing sangs rgyas thob pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)002:2450: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK060(i)002:2451: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK060(i)002:2452: dang po don rtogs mthar mi stong //
NK060(i)002:2453: spyod yul kun tu tshad dpag med //
NK060(i)002:2460: bcu gsum pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:2461: gnyis pa spyod pa la'ang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2463: gzhan sel sgrib pa 'byang zhing bag chags 'dag /don
NK060(i)002:2464: gnyer tshogs rdzogs shing lta sgom bogs 'don par byed
NK060(i)002:2466: sgo gsum don yod par spyod pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2467: ngo bo dmigs bzung thun mong tu bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2468: thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2469: grol lam bag yod kyi spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2472: sems can rtog pa bzlog phyir sman //
NK060(i)002:2473: gtso bor dang du blang bar bya //
NK060(i)002:2475: gnyis pa grol lam la gnyis/
NK060(i)002:2476: cig car ba'i spyod pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2477: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:2478: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po ni //
NK060(i)002:2479: thams cad kun la dbyer med spyod //
NK060(i)002:2481: rim gyis pa'i spyod pa la bdun te/
NK060(i)002:2483: shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa/
NK060(i)002:2484: thabs dang mthun pa'i spyod pa/
NK060(i)002:2491: thos bsam bcu spyod ched du gnyer //
NK060(i)002:2494: gzhan phyir so so'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK060(i)002:2495: don byed ci smos dang po bcu //
NK060(i)002:2496: gzhan la ston cing bkri bar gyis //
NK060(i)002:2499: rgyas pa'i nyer gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:2500: bya ba med pas bya med bya //
NK060(i)002:2501: mi gnas gnas la rnam par spyod //
NK060(i)002:2505: thabs kyi pha rol phyin par spyod //
NK060(i)002:2506: snying rje chud ma zos par bzung //
NK060(i)002:2509: phyogs gcig spyod pa gang gnas pa //
NK060(i)002:2513: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK060(i)002:2514: rnam smin +amo du shes par bya //
NK060(i)002:2515: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK060(i)002:2518: spyod yul lha dang lha mor bslab //
NK060(i)002:2522: gos rgyan bza' btung glu dang tshig /bro gar tshogs kyi sprin phung la //
NK060(i)002:2523: h+aum du shes par rab spyad na //
NK060(i)002:2529: zhes pa'i bar gyis yo byad lnga la spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2531: rnam smin rigs 'dzin gyi spyod pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2532: dkyil 'khor rol pa'i tshul spyod pa //
NK060(i)002:2533: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa bdag gi don //
NK060(i)002:2535: dmigs pas phrin las rdzogs byed pa //
NK060(i)002:2537: zhes pas gzhan don gyi spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2538: tshe dbang gi spyod pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2539: kun tu 'gro ba bdag gi don //
NK060(i)002:2541: bzhi yi thog mas don spyod pa //
NK060(i)002:2542: mkhas la spyod pa'i rigs 'dzin gnas //
NK060(i)002:2543: zhes pas gzhan don gyi spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2544: phyag rgya chen po'i spyod pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2545: lhan cig gnas pas sgrib pa sbyong //
NK060(i)002:2547: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs la //
NK060(i)002:2548: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK060(i)002:2549: ces pas gzhan don spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2550: lhun grub kyi spyod pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2551: nyid phyir rdo rje 'dzin sogs pa //
NK060(i)002:2552: skad cig dus kyi bslab rdzogs nas //
NK060(i)002:2553: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK060(i)002:2554: bcom ldan 'das par gyur pa yun //
NK060(i)002:2556: la lar lhums zhugs bltams pa dang //
NK060(i)002:2557: khab dang rgyal srid bzhes pa dang //
NK060(i)002:2558: zhes pas gzhan don gyi spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2559: zhor gyi skyon yon gong du bstan pa'i dgos ched
NK060(i)002:2560: bzhi yod med kyi rjes su 'gro ldog byed pa'o
NK060(i)002:2571: nyi shu pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:2572: gsum pa dkyil 'khor la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2574: gzhan sel dbang dang sgrub pa'i snod du mi rung ba bsal nas/
NK060(i)002:2576: mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i rten byed do //
NK060(i)002:2578: dkyil la 'khor gyis bskor ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2579: de yang dmigs kyis bkar nas/
NK060(i)002:2582: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum gyi nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:2583: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK060(i)002:2586: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:2587: 'das pa rtag tu dkyil yin te //
NK060(i)002:2592: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum gyi nges tshig ni/
NK060(i)002:2593: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil yin te //
NK060(i)002:2594: rig bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK060(i)002:2596: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi nges tshig ni //
NK060(i)002:2597: snying po thams cad dus su dkyil //
NK060(i)002:2598: gang yang yan lag 'khor du gsungs //
NK060(i)002:2599: bco brgyad khams gsum snying po nyid //
NK060(i)002:2600: de dag 'khor te bde ba'i khams //
NK060(i)002:2601: byang sems bde ba'i ye shes te //
NK060(i)002:2602: brten can ji bzhin rten ji bzhin //
NK060(i)002:2604: ngo bo dang dmigs bzung pa thun mong du bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2606: 'di ni rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK060(i)002:2607: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK060(i)002:2609: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK060(i)002:2612: dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2614: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin no //
NK060(i)002:2616: rang bzhin don dam gyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2617: rgyas pa'i don bzhi pa las/
NK060(i)002:2618: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK060(i)002:2619: chos dbyings bdag dang dbyer med pas //
NK060(i)002:2620: mnyam par sbyor zhing dag pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2622: rang bzhin kun rdzob kyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2624: phyi nang snod bcud dag rnams la //
NK060(i)002:2625: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas //
NK060(i)002:2627: gnyis pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2630: de gnyis ka la yang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga ste/
NK060(i)002:2632: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK060(i)002:2633: yon tan phrin las kun gyi rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:2635: gnyis pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2637: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du byung ba la bzhed/
NK060(i)002:2639: rtog pa phra rags kyi lha yab yum mtshon pa la bzhed de/
NK060(i)002:2640: gnyis ka mthun pa'i lung bzhin/
NK060(i)002:2642: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK060(i)002:2643: chen po rags pa thabs su rtogs //
NK060(i)002:2644: so so'i mtshan nyid shes rab rtogs //
NK060(i)002:2645: gnyis med 'brel pa thabs chen yin //
NK060(i)002:2647: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2648: las dang bya ba lhag pas te/
NK060(i)002:2650: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK060(i)002:2651: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK060(i)002:2652: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK060(i)002:2653: yon tan rnam bcus rgyas zhes bya //
NK060(i)002:2655: dgos ched kyi dbang gis skabs lngar dbye ste/
NK060(i)002:2656: zhi khro'i lha tshogs sgrub cing mchod pa mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)002:2657: dbang bskur ba dbang gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)002:2658: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)002:2659: zhi rgyas dbang drag gis phrin las sgrub pa phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)002:2660: sku gsung thugs kyi rab gnas ni bsod nams rten gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK060(i)002:2661: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2662: rgyas pa'i nyi shu pa las/
NK060(i)002:2664: thams cad dbyings su bsdus nas ni //
NK060(i)002:2665: nyid kyi thugs la thim byas te //
NK060(i)002:2666: thams cad chos sku'i phyag rgya chen //
NK060(i)002:2668: lnga pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2669: bsgom pa'i bya bas lhag pa ste/
NK060(i)002:2674: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du bsgom pa ste/
NK060(i)002:2675: dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i gnyen po'o //
NK060(i)002:2677: snying rje chen po nam mkha' dang mnyam pa bsgom pa ste/
NK060(i)002:2678: stong pa phyang chad du 'dzin pa'i gnyen po'o //
NK060(i)002:2680: stong pa nyid dang snying rje gnyis su med pa'i
NK060(i)002:2681: sku dang ye shes lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa
NK060(i)002:2682: ste/ stong nyid snying rje'am thabs shes rab bam/
NK060(i)002:2683: bden pa gnyis sam snang stong tha dad du 'dzin pa'i gnyen po'o //
NK060(i)002:2685: phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2686: rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'o //
NK060(i)002:2687: lha sku la bslab pa la zhi khro gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:2688: gnyis ka la yang sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsum gsum mo //
NK060(i)002:2692: gsung gi dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i sngags kyis ston/
NK060(i)002:2693: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i phyag rgyas ston no //
NK060(i)002:2694: de bzhin du khro bo'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil
NK060(i)002:2695: 'khor le'u bcu drug pa dang bcu bdun pas ston
NK060(i)002:2696: no // drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2697: phyi byang chub kyi sems rtsa dang rlung /
NK060(i)002:2698: nang byang chub kyi sems thig le/
NK060(i)002:2699: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ye shes so //
NK060(i)002:2700: bdun pa tshoms bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2702: de ltar rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)002:2704: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:2705: rang bzhin gyi snang ba ston pa'i le'u rnams kyis ston/
NK060(i)002:2706: lhag pa gzugs brnyan le'u dgu pas ston/
NK060(i)002:2707: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin le'u bzhi pa/
NK060(i)002:2713: bcu drug pa dang bcu bdun pas ston/
NK060(i)002:2714: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni/
NK060(i)002:2715: le'u gnyis pa dang bcu gsum pas ston/
NK060(i)002:2716: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pas ston/
NK060(i)002:2717: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ston no //
NK060(i)002:2718: bzhi pa dbang la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2720: gzhan sel sgo gsum gyi dri ma dag /don gnyer
NK060(i)002:2721: skal ba dang ldan zhing nus pa dngos su skyed
NK060(i)002:2723: che ba'i yon tan ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2724: ngo bo dang dmigs bzung ba thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2727: rgyu ni yon dbul ba yin te/
NK060(i)002:2728: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK060(i)002:2729: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK060(i)002:2730: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK060(i)002:2731: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK060(i)002:2734: dkyil 'khor khyad par gyis dmigs bzung ba dang /
NK060(i)002:2735: rnam grangs kyi khyad par gyi dmigs bzung ba'o //
NK060(i)002:2737: slob ma tshogs lam pa la slob dpon drod thob
NK060(i)002:2738: pa'i gang zag gis lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK060(i)002:2739: 'khor du dbang bskur/ slob ma mthong sgom gnyis kyi rigs 'dzin la/
NK060(i)002:2740: slob dpon mthar lam pas lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ro //
NK060(i)002:2741: slob ma mthar phyin pa'i lam pa la slob dpon
NK060(i)002:2742: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)002:2744: rnam grangs kyi khyad par gyis dmigs bzung ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2745: dad pa can la phan pa'i dbang bcu/
NK060(i)002:2746: brtson 'grus can la nus pa'i dbang lnga/
NK060(i)002:2747: brtul zhugs can la zab mo'i dbang gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:2749: khro bo'i dbang chog so drug ni/
NK060(i)002:2751: phyi yi dbang ni bcu dang gcig /nang gi dbang ni bcu dang gnyis //
NK060(i)002:2752: gsang dbang bcu dang sgrub dbang gsum //
NK060(i)002:2754: zhor la dus dang skyon yon bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2756: lam gyi sngon 'gro yin pas thog ma dang /
NK060(i)002:2758: lam gyi bogs 'don yin pas dus la nam babs kyi skabs dang /
NK060(i)002:2760: lam lnga mthar phyin nas mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi
NK060(i)002:2761: sa la sbyor ba yin pas tha mar dbang bskur
NK060(i)002:2762: ro // dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni/
NK060(i)002:2764: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK060(i)002:2766: brlag par 'gyur zhes pa'i bar gyis mngon no //
NK060(i)002:2768: dus 'di phyin chad ces pa nas/
NK060(i)002:2769: bdag por 'gyur zhes pa'i bar gyis mngon no //
NK060(i)002:2770: de dag le'u gnyis pa dang /
NK060(i)002:2775: bco lnga pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:2776: lnga pa nges tshig la'ang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2778: gzhan sel ngan song dang theg dman du mi ltung zhing /
NK060(i)002:2779: don gnyer lam gyi ngal ba don can du byed do //
NK060(i)002:2782: gal te 'das na thar pa'i sa bon 'tshig par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2784: sgo gsum gyi srung sdom dam du bcas pa las mi 'da' ba zhig yin no //
NK060(i)002:2785: rnam grangs rnam par dbye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba ni lnga ste/
NK060(i)002:2786: dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni/
NK060(i)002:2787: rgyas pa'i don gcig pa las/
NK060(i)002:2788: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK060(i)002:2789: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK060(i)002:2790: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK060(i)002:2792: dam tshig gi dngos gzhi ni/
NK060(i)002:2794: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK060(i)002:2795: sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig yin //
NK060(i)002:2798: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK060(i)002:2799: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK060(i)002:2800: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:2802: dam tshig gi che ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2803: bla med mchog gi dam tshig ni //
NK060(i)002:2804: 'dul ba'i dbang gi tshul khrims dang //
NK060(i)002:2805: ji snyed sdom pa mtha' yas pa //
NK060(i)002:2806: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /ces so //
NK060(i)002:2807: dam tshig gi rnam grangs ni/
NK060(i)002:2809: smra mi bya zhes pa'i bar gyis rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga/
NK060(i)002:2811: mi 'dor ro zhes pa'i bar gyis yan lag gi dam tshig bcu/
NK060(i)002:2812: de dag las kyang spros na/
NK060(i)002:2813: rtsa ba'i dam tshig ces pa nas/
NK060(i)002:2814: dbye zhes pa'i bar gyis sum brgya drug cur dbye zhing /
NK060(i)002:2816: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu nas //
NK060(i)002:2817: srid gsum 'gro ba ji snyed la //
NK060(i)002:2818: rtog 'dul dam tshig chen por spro //
NK060(i)002:2819: zhes pas brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK060(i)002:2820: zhor la bsrung ba'i dus dang /
NK060(i)002:2821: bskang thabs skyon yon bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2822: dang po dam bcas pa nas/
NK060(i)002:2823: ji srid mthar thug gi 'bras bu ma thob kyi bar du'o //
NK060(i)002:2826: nyams pa'i skyon ni gsum ste/
NK060(i)002:2829: nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i skyon no //
NK060(i)002:2831: rtsa ba'i dam tshig ces rkang pa bzhi'o //
NK060(i)002:2833: yan lag ces rkang pa gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:2835: rtsa ba nyams pa'i zhes rkang pa bzhi'o //
NK060(i)002:2836: dam tshig bsrungs pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)002:2837: rgyal ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa de //
NK060(i)002:2839: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK060(i)002:2840: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlobs //
NK060(i)002:2841: bde gshegs kun gyi yul la zhugs //
NK060(i)002:2842: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK060(i)002:2844: 'di dag le'u bcu dgu pas ston no //
NK060(i)002:2845: drug pa phrin las la'ang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2847: zhi ba'i phrin las kyis phyi ru gdug cig gtum la ma rangs pa rnams dang /
NK060(i)002:2848: nang du rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma zhi bar byed pa'i dgos pa yod/
NK060(i)002:2849: de bzhin du rgyas pas phyi ru 'khor dang longs spyod/
NK060(i)002:2850: nang du tshe dang bsod nams/
NK060(i)002:2852: dbang gis phyi ru gang dbang du bsdu bar 'dod pa/
NK060(i)002:2853: nang du rang gi sems la dbang thob //
NK060(i)002:2854: mngon spyod kyis phyi ru dgra bgegs dang /
NK060(i)002:2855: nang du nyon mongs pa phra rags 'joms pa'i dpa' yod/
NK060(i)002:2857: phrin las bzhis rang gzhan gyi don sgrub pa'i phrin las byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2858: ngo bo dang rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don
NK060(i)002:2859: gyi dmigs bzung ba thun mong du bstan pa la
NK060(i)002:2865: me'i sgo nas phrin las bya ba/
NK060(i)002:2867: dbyibs dang kha dog ces rkang pa bzhis/
NK060(i)002:2868: rdzas kyi sgo nas bya ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2870: bdud rtsi lnga'am zhes rkang pa bzhis/
NK060(i)002:2871: lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas bya ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2872: lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhes rkang pa gsum/
NK060(i)002:2873: mchod rten gdab pa'i sgo nas bya ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2874: rgyas pa'i nyi shu pa las/
NK060(i)002:2876: bgegs kyi ling ga mnan par bya //
NK060(i)002:2878: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2879: phyag rgya bca' ba'i sgo nas bya ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2881: lus ngag snying po gcig tu bsdam //
NK060(i)002:2882: rtse lnga rtse bcu rtse dgu dang //
NK060(i)002:2883: las rnams so so rab tu bsgom //
NK060(i)002:2885: rdo rje dril bu'i sgo nas bya ba ni/
NK060(i)002:2887: rdo rje lan gsum gsor ba yis //
NK060(i)002:2888: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK060(i)002:2893: ljon pa dang ni zhes pa rkang pa gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:2895: dang bas dga' bas zhes rkang pa gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:2896: zhor la dus gang du dgos pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2899: dus ni dbang dang sgrub pa dang //
NK060(i)002:2900: mchod bshags tshe dang dus babs tshe //
NK060(i)002:2902: de dag le'u dgu pa dang bco lnga pa dang nyi shu pas ston no //
NK060(i)002:2903: bdun pa sgrub pa la bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2905: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub myur du 'grub pa'i dgos ched yod do //
NK060(i)002:2907: dngos grub sgrub par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2909: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung nas/
NK060(i)002:2910: bsnyen sgrub bzhi gzhung srong ba zhig yin no //
NK060(i)002:2911: don gyi dmigs bzung ba ni gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2914: thun mongs gi sgrub pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2918: mkha' spyod la sogs pa grub chen brgyad dang /
NK060(i)002:2919: gzhan yang yungs kar rgyal po dang /
NK060(i)002:2922: ro langs bsgrub pa la sogs pa mang du gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)002:2926: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK060(i)002:2927: longs spyod 'byungs zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK060(i)002:2929: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK060(i)002:2933: thams cad stongs shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:2934: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang dgrol //
NK060(i)002:2935: gso dang bsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK060(i)002:2947: gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs kyi/
NK060(i)002:2948: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum dang /
NK060(i)002:2949: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang mos bsgrub pa yin te/
NK060(i)002:2950: de dag gi lung khungs ni/
NK060(i)002:2951: gong du dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su sbyar zin to //
NK060(i)002:2952: zhor la sgrub pa'i dus bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2953: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK060(i)002:2959: bcu gnyis pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:2960: brgyad pa ting nge 'dzin la bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:2962: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub gang sgrub kyang bde blag tu 'grub pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK060(i)002:2964: sems rtse gcig tu zin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:2966: don gyi dmigs bzung ba thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:2968: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK060(i)002:2969: bskyed pa'i rim pa la zhi khro gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:2970: rdzogs pa'i rim pa la mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis so //
NK060(i)002:2971: mtshan bcas la rtsol bcas steng sgo bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)002:2972: rtsol med 'og sgo bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK060(i)002:2974: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin te/
NK060(i)002:2976: zhor la skyon yon bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:2978: rgya mtsho mjing gi pha bong ltar //
NK060(i)002:2979: bskal par lam la 'bad byas kyang //
NK060(i)002:2980: don med snying po bskams pa yin //
NK060(i)002:2982: bsgrub pa'i gtsor ni ting 'dzin pas //
NK060(i)002:2997: nyi shu pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:2998: dgu pa mchod pa la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:3001: don gnyer dbang dang dngos grub 'thob bo //
NK060(i)002:3003: p+au dza'i sgras gnyer bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:3005: yo byad gnas su stobs pa zhig yin la/
NK060(i)002:3006: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung nas/
NK060(i)002:3009: dug gsum gyi mchod pa dang /
NK060(i)002:3010: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa dang /
NK060(i)002:3011: glu ye shes kyi mchod pa tsam las gsal bar ma gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)002:3012: sgrub thabs su yan lag gi rgyud dang bshad pa'i rgyud rnams kyis kha bskangs nas/
NK060(i)002:3013: zhi khro re re la'ang bcu bzhi'am/
NK060(i)002:3015: zhi ba la gus par phyag gi //
NK060(i)002:3028: rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa rnams dang /
NK060(i)002:3029: de bzhin du khro bo la yang /
NK060(i)002:3040: gar gyi mchod pa rnams zhi khro'i sgrub thabs bzhi shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:3041: zhor la mchod pa bya ba'i dus bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:3042: dbang bskur phrin las dam skong tshig /rab gnas lhur len grub pa'i tshe //
NK060(i)002:3048: nyi shu gcig pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3049: bcu pa sngags dang phyag rgya la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:3052: don gnyer tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed do //
NK060(i)002:3054: yid skyob cing byin rlabs 'byung ba'i phyir sngags dang /
NK060(i)002:3055: mdzes shing 'da' bar dka' ba brda sprod pa'i phyir phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)002:3057: ngag gi mthu btsan par byed pa sngags dang /
NK060(i)002:3058: yid ting nge 'dzin las mi 'da' ba zhig phyag rgya yin no //
NK060(i)002:3059: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung na/
NK060(i)002:3063: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba/
NK060(i)002:3065: bzlas pa las kyi sngags so //
NK060(i)002:3066: bskyed sngags la yang zhi khro gnyis las/
NK060(i)002:3067: re re la yang rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK060(i)002:3068: brten pa lha bskyed pa dang /
NK060(i)002:3069: de la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK060(i)002:3071: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab pa dang /
NK060(i)002:3076: rig pa'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK060(i)002:3077: dngos grub bskul ba'i sngags rnams so //
NK060(i)002:3079: rtsa sngags dang bskyed sngags sbrel nas 'dzab tu bzlas pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3080: phyag rgya la rnam grangs mang yang mdor bsdu na/
NK060(i)002:3083: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya dang gsum du 'dus te/
NK060(i)002:3085: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa //
NK060(i)002:3086: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK060(i)002:3089: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog ni //
NK060(i)002:3090: thabs dang shes rab 'byor ldan na //
NK060(i)002:3091: ma bskyod ma bsgul thams cad kun //
NK060(i)002:3092: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK060(i)002:3095: zhi khro'i lha tshogs gtso 'khor gang sgom yang /
NK060(i)002:3101: sku'i phyag rgya chen po bsgom pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3103: dam tshig gi phyag rgya la'ang las dang bsam pa gnyis/
NK060(i)002:3105: bca' ba dang bsam pa gnyis/
NK060(i)002:3106: chos kyi phyag rgya la'ang bsam pa dang brjod pa
NK060(i)002:3107: gnyis de drug /sku'i phyag rgya chen po dang bdun
NK060(i)002:3108: no // de dag ni zhi khro'i phyag rgya'i mchod pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:3111: bcu drug pa bcu bdun pa rnams kyis ston no/
NK060(i)002:3114: gzhan sel phyir rgol sun 'byin zhing /
NK060(i)002:3115: don gnyer rjes 'jug gi lam pa bstan pa la yid ches skyes nas 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod //
NK060(i)002:3117: rgyud gzhung gang zhig /dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel pa dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:3118: ngo bo dang don gyi dmigs bzung ba thun mong du bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:3120: brjod 'brel dgos dang yang dgos dang //
NK060(i)002:3121: rgyu rkyen yan lag bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK060(i)002:3123: rgyud dbu zhabs thams cad kyang dgos 'brel yan lag bzhi ldan du gnas pa yin no //
NK060(i)002:3124: de yang dang po brjod pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:3128: 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las/
NK060(i)002:3129: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK060(i)002:3131: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud do //
NK060(i)002:3133: 'di nyid kyi bcu gsung pa las/
NK060(i)002:3134: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK060(i)002:3135: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK060(i)002:3136: zhes pas mtshon byed yi ge rgyud do //
NK060(i)002:3137: de nyams su blangs pa'i dgos pa ni/
NK060(i)002:3138: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK060(i)002:3139: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK060(i)002:3142: le'u dang po'i bsdu ba las/
NK060(i)002:3143: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phriin las sel med pa yi yon tan yid bzhin rin po che //
NK060(i)002:3144: mi zad par rgyan ldan gyi 'khor lo rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do //
NK060(i)002:3148: shes bya dang shes byed du 'brel la/
NK060(i)002:3149: rjod byed dang dgos pa ni thabs dang thabs byung du 'brel/
NK060(i)002:3150: dgos pa dang nying dgos gnyis de las der byung du 'brel/
NK060(i)002:3151: nying dgos dang brjod bya gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig gi 'brel pa yod do //
NK060(i)002:3152: de dag ni grol lam dbang btsan du byas pa yin gyi/
NK060(i)002:3153: de las gzhan yang thabs lam dbang btsan du byas nas/
NK060(i)002:3154: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni brjod bya/
NK060(i)002:3155: thig le chen po thabs dang bcas pa ni rjod byed/
NK060(i)002:3156: dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha'i bde ba nyams su myong ba ni dgos pa/
NK060(i)002:3157: des ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon du byed pa ni nying dgos so //
NK060(i)002:3158: 'brel pa ni sngar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)002:3160: rgyud dbu zhabs thams cad kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3161: gdams gtad la yang bzhi las/
NK060(i)002:3163: bstan pa'i snying po dar zhing mi nub par byed do //
NK060(i)002:3165: gdams pa yang yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:3166: ngo bo dang dmigs bzung ba thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:3171: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin ni //
NK060(i)002:3172: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK060(i)002:3174: rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams/
NK060(i)002:3176: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor 'dzin //
NK060(i)002:3178: 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams //
NK060(i)002:3179: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK060(i)002:3180: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK060(i)002:3182: lam gyi snang ba bgrod byar gdams //
NK060(i)002:3183: ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byams kyi //
NK060(i)002:3184: don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
NK060(i)002:3186: 'bras bu'i snang ba thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3188: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK060(i)002:3189: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK060(i)002:3190: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK060(i)002:3191: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK060(i)002:3192: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK060(i)002:3194: dar zhing rgyas par bya ba'i phyir sdud pa po la gtad/
NK060(i)002:3195: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK060(i)002:3196: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK060(i)002:3197: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK060(i)002:3198: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:3199: de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK060(i)002:3200: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK060(i)002:3201: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK060(i)002:3203: mi nub par bya ba'i phyir gang zag chos kyi mig can la gtad/
NK060(i)002:3204: rgyas pa'i lnga bcu pa las/
NK060(i)002:3205: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK060(i)002:3206: phyogs bcu kun tu spel ba dang //
NK060(i)002:3207: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK060(i)002:3208: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK060(i)002:3210: byin che bar bya ba'i phyir ma mo dang mkha' 'gro la gtad do //
NK060(i)002:3211: 'di nyid kyi le'u tha mas ston no //
NK060(i)002:3212: dbang po tha ma la 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas bsnyad pa ni/
NK060(i)002:3214: gang la lta dang sgo 'byed pa //
NK060(i)002:3216: rkyen dang gzhan dmigs 'dzin pa'i tshig /ma bcos me long s+n+rel gzhi rnams //
NK060(i)002:3217: me long bcu dang mthun sbyar nas //
NK060(i)002:3218: tshig don rnam par sbyar ba yin //
NK060(i)002:3220: bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las/
NK060(i)002:3221: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig khyung nam mkha' la lding ba lta bur bshad/
NK060(i)002:3222: rnam par 'byed pa'i tshig stag gi mchongs pa/
NK060(i)002:3223: spyi don sdud pa'i tshig seng ge chen po'i mchongs pa/
NK060(i)002:3224: 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros/
NK060(i)002:3225: rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig rus sbal gyi nur 'gros/
NK060(i)002:3226: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig rna phrug brag la 'dzeg pa/
NK060(i)002:3227: gtar kha gegs sel gyi tshig glag mo gzan la 'jum pa/
NK060(i)002:3228: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig dus kyi 'brug sgra/
NK060(i)002:3229: mtshon pa dpe'i tshig me long g.ya' dag pa/
NK060(i)002:3230: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig seng ge'i phru gu rtsal sbyong ba ltar du bshad pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3232: khyung nam mkha' la lding ba'i tshe mig gyen la mi blta gshog pa rlob pa'i rtsol ba med/
NK060(i)002:3233: ngam grog dang g.yang sa la nyam mi nga /
NK060(i)002:3234: bya lam la rjes med pa bzhin/
NK060(i)002:3235: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig gis theg pa thams cad khog 'og tu 'jug /lam bgrod pa'i rtsol ba med/
NK060(i)002:3236: srid pa dang zhi ba la nyam mi nga /
NK060(i)002:3237: blta bya lta byed blo yul du byed pa'i rtog pa med pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3238: lta ba ston pa'i le'u gsum pa/
NK060(i)002:3249: nyer gnyis pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3252: bgrod par bya ba'i sa tshigs dum bu dum bur
NK060(i)002:3253: bcad nas mchongs pa bzhin rnam par dbye ba'i tshig
NK060(i)002:3254: gis/ tshig dang don gyi dmigs so sor phye nas ming 'dogs gsal bar ston pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3256: seng ge chen po mchongs pa'i dus na/
NK060(i)002:3257: mchongs pa gcig gi khog 'og tu sa tshigs du ma chud pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3258: spyi don bsdu ba'i tshig gis tshigs dang don gyi
NK060(i)002:3259: rnams grangs du ma'ang don gyi ngo bo gcig tu
NK060(i)002:3264: drug pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3266: bya ngang mo 'gro ba'i tshe phyir rjes kyis sngar rjes non par 'gro ba bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3267: 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig gis tshig 'brel dang don 'grel ma chad par 'grel sbyor ba'o //
NK060(i)002:3269: rus sbal 'gro ba'i tshe g.yo 'gul mi mngon par shugs kyis 'gro zhing /
NK060(i)002:3270: sa stong mi ldas par rjes kyis khyab pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3271: rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig gi 'bru stong mi ldas par tshig don brda sprod par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3272: de ltar sa gcod pa dang 'brel sbyor ba dang 'bru bsnon pa dang gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:3273: spyi 'gro rnam pa gsum zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)002:3274: gzhung dbu zhabs thams cad la sbyor ba shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)002:3276: rna phrug bral la 'dzeg pa'i tshe/
NK060(i)002:3277: skyes ma thag tu brag me long gi ngos lta bur rtsed mo rtse zhing 'gro ba'i tshe/
NK060(i)002:3278: rig dwags gzhan la mi 'tshams kyang rna phrug rang la 'tshams pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3279: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig gis zab lam sbas tshul du bstan pa ni/
NK060(i)002:3280: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud man chod du mi 'tshams kyang
NK060(i)002:3281: rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud nyams su len pa
NK060(i)002:3292: nyi shu pa rnams kyis rten no //
NK060(i)002:3294: glag mo gzan la 'dzums pa'i tshi/
NK060(i)002:3295: gang yid la btags pa de yi khong gi bcud 'byin par byed pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3296: gtar kha gegs sel gyi tshig gis grub mtha'i don lon par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3297: de dag gang gis ston na/
NK060(i)002:3303: bcu dgu pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3305: dpyid kyi dus su 'brug gi sgra byung bas/
NK060(i)002:3306: skye bo rnams de ring nas dbyar dgun bye'o zhes dus tshod kyi spros pa chod pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3307: bka' lung tshad ma la brten nas don sgro 'dogs chod par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3313: bcu gsum pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3315: me long gi nang du byad bzhin gyi skyon yon
NK060(i)002:3316: ngos zin pa bzhin shin tu lkog gyur gyi don
NK060(i)002:3317: rnams kyang thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK060(i)002:3318: dpes mtshon nas nges par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3327: nyi shu pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3329: seng ge'i phrug gu rtsal sbyong ba'i tshe na/
NK060(i)002:3330: bsnol mar mchongs nas drang por 'gro ba bzhin du
NK060(i)002:3331: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig gis don gyi 'khrug
NK060(i)002:3332: sdeb/ dkyus kyi go rim brjes/
NK060(i)002:3334: sgra ji bzhin pa ma yin/
NK060(i)002:3335: don thun mong ba ma yin pa'i rgyud don phyin cig ma log par ston pa'o //
NK060(i)002:3344: nyi shu pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3345: spyi don gsum pa 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba 'bras bu thob tshul dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)002:3346: rgyas pa'i re bdun pa las/
NK060(i)002:3347: sku mchog rdo rje 'od snang ba //
NK060(i)002:3348: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:3351: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)002:3353: dgos ched ni bdag gzhan gyi mdzad pa ma lus par rdzogs par byed do //
NK060(i)002:3355: smin pa'am mthar phyin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)002:3357: ma 'dres rnam grangs kyi ngo bo dang /
NK060(i)002:3358: dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngo bo'o //
NK060(i)002:3360: 'di nyid kyi bcu bzhi pa las/
NK060(i)002:3361: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK060(i)002:3362: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK060(i)002:3365: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK060(i)002:3366: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK060(i)002:3368: don gyi dmigs bzung ba ni gnyis te/
NK060(i)002:3369: theg pa thun mong gi 'bras bu sku gsum ni/
NK060(i)002:3371: chos sku dpag med ces pa nas/
NK060(i)002:3372: bsam mi khyab ces pa'i bar ro //
NK060(i)002:3373: theg pa mchog gi 'bras bu ni sku lnga ste/
NK060(i)002:3374: skye shi med pa'i zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)002:3375: kun kyang rdzogs chen pa'i bar ro //
NK060(i)002:3376: de lta bu'i 'bras bu'i thob tshul ni/
NK060(i)002:3378: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK060(i)002:3379: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK060(i)002:3380: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK060(i)002:3381: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK060(i)002:3384: spyir sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa dang /
NK060(i)002:3385: khyad par du gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyud 'di nyid
NK060(i)002:3386: kyis don mdzad pa gnyis ka'i tshul ni gsum du
NK060(i)002:3387: byung ste/ rten can gyi don byed par 'dod pa bram ze mchod sdong sgrub pa lta bu/
NK060(i)002:3388: rten med kyi don bsgrub par 'dod pa drang sroong dmod pa sgrub pa lta bu/
NK060(i)002:3389: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi don byed par 'dod
NK060(i)002:3390: pa yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta
NK060(i)002:3391: bu dang gsum las/ lugs dang po ni/
NK060(i)002:3392: dper na rigs sngags grub pa'i bram ze zhig gis rin po che'i mchod sdong bsgrubs nas bzhag pas/
NK060(i)002:3393: bram ze kho rang tshe'i dus byas kyang kho'i rjes
NK060(i)002:3394: 'jug rnams kyi 'dod pa rnams rin po che'i mchod
NK060(i)002:3395: sdong gis skong bar byed pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3396: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rlabs po che tshogs
NK060(i)002:3397: gnyis yongs su rdzogs par byas nas mi dmigs pa'i
NK060(i)002:3398: dbyings su yongs su mya ngan las 'das kyang /
NK060(i)002:3399: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)002:3400: kyi gdul bya rnams kyi don byed par 'dod pa
NK060(i)002:3401: ni/ rgya gar du slob dpon seng ge bzang po dang /
NK060(i)002:3402: bod na zhang shes rab bla ma la sogs pa'i bzhed pa yin no //
NK060(i)002:3405: dmod pa grub pa'i drang srong zhig gis dmod pa bsgrubs nas bzhag pas/
NK060(i)002:3406: drang srong kho rang tshe'i dus byas kyang gzhan snang
NK060(i)002:3407: du kho'i dmod pa ji lta bar 'byung ba bzhin
NK060(i)002:3408: du/ byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa'i dus
NK060(i)002:3409: su smon lam rgya chen po btab pa'i mthus gdul
NK060(i)002:3410: bya rnams kyi snang ngor de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku
NK060(i)002:3411: gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa gdul bya gang la gang
NK060(i)002:3412: 'dul de la der bstan pa ltar snang bar zad
NK060(i)002:3413: du/ kyi/ byang chub sems dpa' mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i dus na/
NK060(i)002:3414: yul yul can gyi gzung 'dzin bag la nyal gnyen
NK060(i)002:3415: po rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bcom
NK060(i)002:3416: nas rig pa rgyun chad pa'i phyir ye shes kyang
NK060(i)002:3418: rgya gar na slob dpon chen po klu sgrub dang /
NK060(i)002:3419: bod na rong zom chos kyi bzang po la sogs pa'i bzhed pa yin no //
NK060(i)002:3421: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags nas mchod na/
NK060(i)002:3422: 'gro ba rang gi bsod nams dang 'tshams pa'i dgos 'dod 'byung mod kyang /
NK060(i)002:3423: rin po che la rtsol rtog dang nye ring med pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)002:3424: rang gi sems kyi chos nyid chos dbyings shin tu
NK060(i)002:3425: dri med kyi chos sku glo bur gyi dri mas
NK060(i)002:3426: bsgribs pa lam lnga sa bcu mthar phyin pas dag
NK060(i)002:3427: nas/ ngo bo nyid kyi sku mngon du byas pa
NK060(i)002:3428: rgyu mthun zab pa'i chos sku'i yon tan gyi cha
NK060(i)002:3429: las gzugs sku gnyis kyi phrin las kyis/
NK060(i)002:3430: gdul bya gang la gang 'dul de la der snang nas/
NK060(i)002:3432: rgya gar du mkhas pa chen po sh+r+ai sing ha dang /
NK060(i)002:3433: bod na zur chung shes rab grags pa la sogs pa'i bzhed pa yin no //
NK060(i)002:3434: 'di dag le'u gang gis ston na/
NK060(i)002:3435: le'u dang po dang gnyis pa'i stod la sogs pa 'bras bu ston pa'i le'u rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)002:3436: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK060(i)002:3437: rgyud kyi khog dbub rin cen 'bar ba'i gur zhes
NK060(i)002:3438: bya ba 'di ni/ bla ma gong ma rnams kyis
NK060(i)002:3439: mdzad pa'i yig cha la rten bcas nas chos smra
NK060(i)002:3440: ba'i sngags 'chang bsam grub rdo rjees zur tsam bcos
NK060(i)002:3441: te dag cing legs par bgyis pa'o //
